{"1":[[100,210,"I cheated on my fiance."],[280,370,"Three years ago,"],[393,520,"on my engagement day,"],[583,703,"I found out my fiancé"],[706,806,"was seeing someone else."],[880,1003,"I got wasted,"],[1060,1180,"and somehow slept with this man"],[1183,1353,"named Robert Cooper."],[1433,1510,"Ever since,"],[1576,1713,"I've been blindfolded,"],[1716,1930,"being his secret mistress for three years."],[2560,2636,"Sit down."],[4723,4786,"Wait."],[4823,4933,"Not here."],[5016,5119,"Then where?"],[5196,5306,"I'm getting married."],[5390,5513,"Don't leave any love bite."],[5653,5740,"What do you mean?"],[5803,5934,"Didn't you promise me"],[5983,6193,"you'd let me go after 3 years?"],[6243,6373,"Next time we meet,"],[6423,6553,"we should act like strangers."],[6663,6823,"That would be the best ending."],[7083,7190,"It's not over."],[7310,7460,"Tonight has just begun."],[8743,8790,"Sir."],[8803,8873,"Your Dad plans to let"],[8873,9006,"Gavin inherit the Sinclair Group."],[9010,9230,"But he has to marry Anne."],[9283,9420,"If inheriting is such a hassle,"],[9445,9566,"then he shouldn't bother."],[9636,9743,"Notify the press."],[9840,9953,"Tell them I'm back."],[10192,10373,"Gavin, what should we have for lunch?"],[10420,10580,"Anything is fine as long as I'm with you."],[10913,11043,"Why are you at the office?"],[11083,11200,"Uncle Arman is coming back today."],[11203,11306,"Grandpa called me"],[11310,11450,"to take you home right away."],[11473,11623,"He hasn't been back in three years."],[11626,11783,"Why the sudden return now?"],[12560,12753,"Grandpa took you in only because"],[12753,12920,"a psychic said you'd bring us luck."],[12923,13036,"Don't forget it."],[13050,13240,"Three years ago, I risked my life"],[13253,13476,"to get you to the hospital and save you."],[13490,13680,"His return right now puts me in a tough spot."],[13713,13850,"Don't be ungrateful."],[13932,14133,"You don't need to remind me every second."],[14153,14250,"I won't forget."],[14326,14403,"Let's go."],[14480,14710,"Gavin, you promised me."],[14710,14943,"Even if you marry Anne, you won't touch her."],[14980,15186,"Don't worry, I won't touch her."],[15414,15670,"Anne, I'm a clean freak."],[15674,15844,"I don't like others touching my things."],[16170,16253,"Your things? He's mine."],[16253,16460,"Miss Blake, you have no shame?"],[16490,16536,"You!"],[16540,16783,"Don't worry. Not only am I a clean freak,"],[16799,16920,"I also have good manners."],[16933,17166,"I won't steal others' men like you."],[17676,17780,"Gavin,"],[17833,18040,"once you successfully inherit Sinclair Group,"],[18070,18216,"the debt I owe you for saving my life"],[18220,18356,"will be paid off, right?"],[19683,19763,"Anne."],[19780,19903,"Don't even think about leaving me,"],[19950,20130,"even if I show you my true face."],[21134,21240,"Uncle Arman."]],"2":[[173,366,"Uncle Arman, what brings you back?"],[366,582,"It sounds like I'm not exactly welcome here."],[700,786,"Not at all."],[813,920,"His voice..."],[923,1090,"Why does it sound so much like Devil Robert's?"],[1323,1526,"What? Have you forgotten your manners?"],[1720,1796,"Uncle Arman."],[1870,1983,"Nice dress."],[2003,2093,"It fits you perfectly."],[2173,2323,"It doesn't look like Gavin's taste."],[2596,2780,"Did another man buy it for you?"],[3223,3403,"Just wear the clothes I gave you for now."],[3873,3983,"How did he know?"],[4052,4236,"I remember when you left,"],[4250,4436,"you weren't wearing this dress."],[4453,4650,"While I was waiting for you,"],[4653,4786,"my dress accidentally got snagged."],[4823,5153,"So I just bought one in the mall."],[5156,5343,"So, the Sinclairs are finally treating you well."],[5360,5490,"Now you can casually afford"],[5493,5660,"a couture dress worth 200k."],[5843,5983,"200k?"],[6223,6470,"Anne, where did you get the money"],[6486,6660,"to buy such an expensive dress?"],[6903,7103,"It's a knockoff."],[7253,7510,"F*ck, I bought an expensive dress for her."],[7530,7663,"But she called it a knockoff."],[7850,8020,"The Sinclairs' future granddaughter-in-law"],[8063,8163,"wearing a knockoff"],[8163,8316,"would sound terrible if word got out."],[8450,8496,"Come here."],[8506,8546,"Huh?"],[8746,8823,"Come here."],[9383,9573,"Gavin didn't buy nice dresses for you."],[9630,9743,"I will buy it for you."],[9836,9913,"Here, swipe my card."],[10053,10410,"I never offended him, right?"],[10893,11200,"Uncle Arman, Anne is my fiancée."],[11236,11510,"It's not your place to give her money."],[11663,11826,"I'm teaching you a lesson."],[11880,12120,"If you don't cherish your things,"],[12153,12313,"someone else is bound to come and take it."],[13360,13470,"What's wrong with you?"],[13500,13666,"You're the future Mrs. Sinclair!"],[13670,13806,"How can you go out wearing a knockoff?"],[13810,13986,"Don't you care about the Sinclair reputation?"],[14180,14413,"You're so vain."],[14416,14530,"You like designer brands, right?"],[14616,14806,"Go buy it with my money!"],[14956,15050,"You're going too far."],[15083,15290,"I'm disciplining my fiancée."],[15293,15463,"You're overstepping your bounds."],[15960,16116,"What's the fuss?"]],"3":[[126,280,"What's the fuss?"],[730,826,"Grandpa."],[930,1193,"Your grandson was about to hit his fiancée,"],[1244,1367,"so I stepped in to teach him a lesson."],[1523,1713,"Grandpa, it's all a misunderstanding."],[1743,1783,"Hmph."],[1880,1956,"Arman,"],[1973,2123,"didn't you say on the phone"],[2126,2310,"you have a girlfriend?"],[2353,2463,"Why didn't you bring her back?"],[2490,2700,"Uncle Arman has a girlfriend?"],[2706,2856,"What's her family background?"],[3053,3226,"She can't be seen in public right now."],[3233,3336,"So it's not convenient to bring her home."],[3340,3456,"What's the situation?"],[3480,3576,"Why can't your girlfriend"],[3580,3706,"be seen in public?"],[3706,3870,"She is someone else's girlfriend right now."],[3910,4310,"You mean you're a homewrecker now?"],[4383,4616,"Being a homewrecker and cuckolding others"],[4730,4823,"is better than someone"],[4823,4950,"cuckolding me."],[4953,5030,"You!"],[5130,5413,"He's truly the Sinclair family's most willful"],[5413,5616,"and reckless Mr. Badass."],[5670,5826,"You are an absolute disgrace!"],[5983,6150,"Grandpa, calm down."],[6180,6346,"Uncle Arman has always been like this."],[6346,6493,"You know how he is."],[6493,6766,"Cut ties with all those hookers outside."],[6793,6966,"Otherwise, don't bother coming back!"],[7786,8053,"A Sinclair man being a homewrecker"],[8093,8303,"doesn't sound good if word gets out."],[8603,8796,"You'd better worry about yourself."],[8873,9170,"It looks like you're the one being cuckolded."],[10193,10366,"What did you do with Arman?"],[10370,10533,"What did he mean by that?"],[10580,10956,"Did you hook up with him?"],[11023,11130,"What are you talking about?"],[11130,11223,"That's impossible."],[11226,11353,"Behave yourself."],[11356,11450,"Don't betray me,"],[11490,11676,"or I'll make you wish you were dead."]],"4":[[343,446,"It's so expensive."],[583,733,"How is he so rich?"],[932,1062,"These clothes..."],[1113,1193,"No."],[1230,1393,"I have to get rid of them."],[1943,2103,"There's a meteor shower tonight."],[2103,2206,"Want to watch it together?"],[2663,2930,"No, don't contact me again."],[3438,3562,"Where are the stars?"],[4416,4516,"You're here to watch the stars?"],[4666,4770,"U-Uncle Arman."],[4990,5190,"Why so nervous?"],[5210,5373,"Did you arrange to meet your secret lover"],[5413,5543,"to watch the stars?"],[5603,5746,"How did he know?"],[5913,6020,"Did I guess right?"],[6150,6230,"No."],[6253,6393,"I just suddenly wanted to come out"],[6393,6520,"to see if there were any stars."],[6520,6643,"It's going to rain tonight."],[6770,6871,"Next time you plan a date with a lover"],[6872,6982,"to watch the stars,"],[7033,7156,"remember to check the weather forecast."],[7516,7746,"Why is he so sure?"],[7853,7950,"Uncle Arman,"],[7973,8263,"teasing your nephew's wife"],[8283,8393,"made you feel amused?"],[9243,9350,"Nephew's wife?"],[9457,9534,"Are you sure?"],[9888,10052,"Don't you think my voice"],[10123,10216,"sounds familiar?"]],"5":[[293,436,"It's getting late."],[450,540,"Gavin and I have to"],[540,660,"go to school tomorrow."],[676,850,"You should get some rest, Uncle Arman."],[1696,1790,"Do me a favor."],[2350,2566,"Gavin, I crashed the car."],[2568,2653,"Don't be scared."],[2653,2760,"I'll be right there."],[2770,2793,"Hey!"],[2946,3050,"Grace was in a car accident."],[3050,3146,"I need to go check on her."],[3146,3237,"Go to school by yourself."],[3239,3362,"Don't tell Grandpa about this."],[3411,3450,"Gavin..."],[3979,4116,"You poor little thing."],[4176,4276,"Your fiancé left you behind"],[4276,4382,"to go find his lover."],[4657,4830,"Are you going to look for your lover too?"],[4890,5177,"Uncle Arman, since yesterday,"],[5179,5362,"you've been saying I have a lover."],[5386,5493,"Do you have any proof?"],[5655,5865,"Get in. I'll drive you."],[5970,6087,"You got played."],[6356,6436,"What?"],[6986,7110,"Do you want me to send the evidence"],[7206,7326,"straight to the old man?"],[8793,9100,"What evidence do you actually have?"],[9333,9490,"Are you really messing around with men?"],[9980,10194,"What exactly do you want?"],[10546,10852,"I like you."],[11206,11300,"Uncle Arman,"],[11350,11573,"I'm your nephew's wife now."],[11596,11736,"Please behave yourself."],[12006,12260,"Don't you just want to become Madam Sinclair?"],[12260,12400,"You with the best luck,"],[12400,12610,"paired with the Sinclair family's favorite son."],[12616,12723,"A perfect match."],[12778,12890,"Isn't that better than"],[12890,13166,"marrying that stupid and heartless Gavin?"],[14210,14263,"Yes."],[14300,14520,"I want to be hostess of the Sinclair family."],[14520,14734,"But the one who can make me Mrs. Sinclair"],[14743,14900,"can only be Gavin."]],"6":[[10,233,"Uncle Arman, if you want to vie for power,"],[263,413,"just do it openly."],[443,593,"Stealing your nephew's fiancée"],[686,843,"is simply disgraceful."],[850,996,"You think that's disgraceful?"],[1076,1280,"I can stoop much lower."],[1430,1616,"If you dare to marry Gavin,"],[1680,1786,"I will expose the fact"],[1790,2030,"that you've been cheating on him."],[2540,2616,"Fine."],[2696,2860,"We'll see about that."],[3476,3633,"I'll give you a day to think it over."],[3873,4023,"Give me your answer when you're ready."],[4713,4780,"Anne Sinclair."],[4793,4946,"Leaving my side"],[4950,5066,"is not up to you."],[5640,5746,"Have you thought it over?"],[5816,5920,"No need."],[5976,6123,"I will only marry Gavin."],[6280,6436,"What exactly do you see in me?"],[6870,6946,"You're sexy."],[7170,7280,"I'm not sexy."],[7333,7460,"You don't need to keep finding excuses"],[7463,7556,"to hit on me."],[7643,7733,"Anne."],[7766,7876,"Anne?"],[8003,8126,"What are you two doing over there?"],[8230,8520,"Grandpa, I ran into Uncle Arman."],[8520,8713,"We were just chatting."],[8716,8950,"I invited the President of Star Orphanage"],[8956,9066,"to come over this Saturday"],[9070,9266,"to discuss your wedding with Gavin."],[9283,9396,"The President is coming?"],[9400,9476,"Yes."],[9503,9666,"You grew up in the orphanage"],[9670,9886,"and entered the Sinclair family at eight."],[9890,10086,"The President is like a mother to you."],[10086,10180,"For your wedding,"],[10180,10373,"we must tell her."],[10473,10600,"Thank you, Grandpa."],[10633,10850,"Arman, as an elder,"],[10853,11010,"you should entertain the guests on Saturday."],[11013,11220,"Take care of Anne and Gavin."],[11220,11296,"Sure."],[11423,11570,"I'll definitely be there."]],"7":[[1246,1400,"I hope you won't be too surprised."],[1603,1713,"Oh, you're too kind."],[1726,1810,"President."],[1956,2006,"President."],[2006,2080,"Anne."],[2103,2246,"Oh, look at how you've changed."],[2246,2430,"I almost didn't recognize you."],[2430,2453,"Hey,"],[2453,2540,"Gavin,"],[2540,2706,"don't you recognize President Adams?"],[2830,2880,"President Adams."],[2906,2936,"Hello."],[3056,3156,"Come, have a seat."],[3320,3502,"Anne, since you've graduated,"],[3520,3720,"here is a graduation gift for you."],[3720,3836,"Thank you, President."],[3876,3960,"You're welcome."],[3960,4043,"President Adams,"],[4082,4206,"Anne only gets very happy"],[4206,4323,"when she is with you."],[4323,4466,"She acts more like a child then."],[4466,4566,"Chairman Sinclair, you've raised Anne"],[4566,4690,"to be such an outstanding girl."],[4690,4863,"That is truly her good fortune."],[4866,4983,"Anne is a good kid,"],[5020,5133,"and indeed very outstanding."],[5133,5496,"Gavin is so lucky to marry her later."],[5639,5850,"Is everyone here? Let's serve the food."],[5853,5880,"Wait."],[5943,6010,"Where's your uncle?"],[6010,6141,"I just called him,"],[6148,6273,"and he said he was here."],[6316,6423,"Why hasn't he come in yet?"],[6423,6550,"Grandpa,"],[6550,6843,"Uncle Arman is probably busy with work."],[6856,7030,"It's fine if he can't make it."],[7053,7089,"Heh."],[7146,7257,"It's best if he doesn't come."],[7264,7396,"This is absolutely outrageous."],[7448,7566,"I'll give him another call."],[7700,7856,"Everyone is here,"],[7856,7970,"waiting for you."],[8001,8081,"What did you say?"],[8240,8396,"You want Anne to take the call?"],[8510,8570,"Anne,"],[8623,8773,"Arman wants to speak with you."],[9016,9063,"Hello?"],[9063,9150,"Uncle Arman."],[9256,9320,"Oh."],[9320,9456,"Something came up and you can't make it?"],[9463,9686,"That's alright. You handle your business."],[9796,9883,"Anne."],[12853,12956,"Could it be that"],[13003,13144,"he's really Devil Robert?"]],"8":[[2146,2176,"Whoa."],[2263,2360,"You're awake."],[2430,2520,"Who are you?"],[2673,2846,"Last night, you asked to sleep with me."],[2950,3040,"I'm sorry."],[3050,3223,"I had too much to drink last night."],[3527,3634,"Wait, wait."],[3650,3952,"Being drunk is no excuse for harassing me."],[4093,4250,"Don't you plan to take responsibility?"],[4306,4430,"How much do you want?"],[4503,4533,"Hah."],[4953,5126,"I want you to be my lover."],[5223,5433,"I already have a fiancé."],[5680,5876,"Didn't your fiancé cheat on you too?"],[5930,6006,"Am I right?"],[6450,6563,"I'm not ready yet."],[6613,6756,"If you don't agree,"],[6850,7086,"I'll expose everything about us."],[7386,7540,"Then I'll take that as a yes."],[8030,8293,"How can Devil Robert be Arman?"],[8346,8540,"Who's calling? Why aren't you answering?"],[8630,8796,"Didn't I tell you?"],[8810,8933,"It's your future daughter-in-law."],[8943,9090,"Didn't I tell you long ago?"],[9090,9263,"Cut ties with that woman."],[9266,9516,"I can't. She's the only one I'll marry."],[9773,9943,"Grandpa, Uncle Arman."],[9950,10140,"We're here today to discuss"],[10143,10326,"my wedding with Gavin."],[10340,10516,"Let's eat first."],[10523,10600,"Hmm."],[10650,10763,"Anne is right."],[10766,10943,"We'll discuss your issues later."],[10963,11076,"Look at you."],[11076,11223,"President Adams has waited for so long."],[11226,11513,"Mr. Sinclair must be busy with work."],[11513,11646,"It's my honor to meet him."],[11646,11716,"Hahaha."]],"9":[[170,316,"She can't have cold drinks right now."],[336,443,"Switch it for something hot."],[674,776,"Uncle Arman, how do you know"],[776,896,"she can't have cold drinks?"],[1036,1150,"I went downstairs last night"],[1153,1263,"to get some water."],[1263,1406,"I bumped into Uncle Arman."],[1436,1576,"He offered me ice water."],[1576,1840,"I told him I was on my period."],[1996,2103,"Is that so?"],[2106,2196,"If Anne says so,"],[2200,2306,"then it must be true."],[2356,2480,"As her fiancé,"],[2480,2633,"how do you know less than I do"],[2633,2793,"about your fiancée's body?"],[3243,3320,"Anne,"],[3380,3623,"I've been so busy with work lately."],[3626,3740,"I've neglected you."],[3760,3843,"It's okay."],[4016,4336,"Just eat. No one wants to see you acting here."],[4420,4613,"Uncle Arman, what do you mean?"],[4640,4893,"Anne and I are childhood sweethearts."],[4896,5043,"Everyone knows our bond."],[5283,5360,"Really?"],[5813,5990,"Uncle Arman, I know."],[5993,6130,"You're upset as Gavin and I"],[6130,6253,"haven't treated you to dinner"],[6260,6446,"since you returned."],[6446,6596,"So over this meal today,"],[6620,6726,"we'd like to toast you."],[6806,7100,"Please forgive us."],[7703,7780,"Fine."],[7886,8053,"Since your love runs so deep,"],[8056,8210,"to give you more time to date,"],[8296,8446,"I've decided to manage the Sinclair Group."],[8506,8740,"So Gavin has more time for romance."],[8763,8950,"Arman, are you serious?"],[8963,9210,"Great! The Sinclair Group welcomes you!"],[9246,9343,"Hahaha!"],[9363,9440,"Gavin,"],[9563,9680,"you're not afraid I'll take your position, are you?"],[9713,9906,"What's this nonsense about taking positions?"],[9906,10183,"With the two of you managing the company,"],[10186,10363,"it couldn't be better."],[10406,10540,"Grandpa is right."],[10560,10786,"To run the company with Uncle Arman,"],[10793,10916,"I couldn't be happier."],[10916,11130,"President Adams, have a drink."],[11273,11566,"No, Gavin is being too obvious."],[11621,11826,"Grandpa is sure to get upset."],[11946,12200,"Gavin, stop drinking."],[12266,12370,"Leave me alone!"],[12593,12780,"I'm fine. I need to go to the restroom."]],"10":[[403,466,"Ah!"],[616,786,"U-Uncle Arman."],[880,950,"Why are you looking at me"],[950,1076,"like you've seen a ghost?"],[1100,1220,"Is there a difference?"],[1402,1450,"No."],[1453,1536,"I'm done freshening up."],[1536,1626,"I should go back."],[2210,2356,"You're leaving in such a hurry."],[2413,2600,"Seeing me will remind you"],[2620,2780,"of your sexy position in bed?"],[2926,3116,"Or are you afraid our affair"],[3166,3256,"will be discovered?"],[3440,3576,"I didn't know it was you."],[3620,3786,"If I had known, I..."],[3793,3893,"If you had known,"],[4030,4296,"would you have been more passionate?"],[4326,4623,"Didn't you go abroad three years ago?"],[4640,4790,"But that didn't stop me"],[4820,4983,"from flying back every week"],[5020,5113,"to sleep with you."],[5196,5373,"He actually flew back"],[5374,5570,"from abroad every week."],[5716,5810,"I..."],[5833,6030,"I'm getting married soon."],[6087,6276,"Let's just forget everything that happened,"],[6409,6673,"okay?"],[7156,7236,"I can't."],[7307,7640,"I can't forget you holding me in bed,"],[7840,7966,"looking all flushed."],[8619,8736,"Then what do you want?"],[9036,9253,"Kiss me, and I'll tell you."],[9420,9500,"Wait."],[9706,9806,"Not here."],[9900,10016,"Then where?"],[10030,10153,"I'm getting married."],[10280,10386,"Don't leave any love bite."],[10766,10863,"Don't do this."],[11280,11483,"Anne, are you done?"],[11483,11620,"Did you see Uncle Arman?"],[11693,11746,"Alright."],[11746,11856,"I'll be right there."]],"11":[[1138,1228,"I'm sorry."],[1720,1810,"Anne!"],[1863,2040,"What the hell are you doing in there?"],[3030,3130,"Anne Sinclair."],[3216,3356,"I'd like to see"],[3433,3593,"if your love for Gavin"],[3634,3817,"is truly unbreakable."],[4193,4356,"What were you doing in there?"],[4370,4463,"You took forever."],[4530,4623,"My clothes got dirty,"],[4623,4716,"so I was cleaning them."],[4766,4913,"Also, I'm on my period."],[4940,5060,"I have a stomachache."],[5096,5343,"Anne, back at the dinner table,"],[5346,5587,"I saw you making eyes at Arman."],[5597,5678,"Don't forget it."],[5680,5900,"He is fighting me for the inheritance."],[5935,6060,"And remember this,"],[6096,6343,"only I care about you in this family."],[6400,6606,"I risked my life to save you."],[6623,6740,"Otherwise, you'd be dead."],[6743,6880,"And there would just be a second \"Anne\""],[6883,7000,"to take your place."],[7346,7533,"Gavin is paranoid by nature."],[7580,7843,"I really need to keep my distance from Arman."],[8210,8400,"Gavin, Anne."],[8453,8642,"Show President Adams around."],[8643,8686,"Sure."],[8686,8780,"The kids are busy."],[8780,8890,"No need to trouble them."],[8890,9096,"It's fine, President. I'll walk with you."],[9156,9313,"President Adams, you're actually like"],[9313,9473,"a mother to Anne."],[9473,9563,"At a time like this,"],[9563,9726,"you should hang out with her"],[9726,9893,"and shop for wedding things."],[9986,10073,"Alright."],[10153,10270,"I'll be going now."],[10313,10370,"Goodbye, Grandpa."],[10370,10410,"Okay."],[10793,10976,"At the wedding,"],[10980,11110,"all the guests are the Sinclair family's"],[11116,11226,"relatives and friends."],[11233,11403,"President Adams doesn't know them."],[11403,11543,"Why not let her leave?"],[11550,11653,"You know, to avoid any embarrassment."],[11740,11913,"It's fine. I... I can..."],[11913,12200,"Don't you agree, President Adams?"],[12476,12576,"You're right."],[12633,12756,"Actually, the kids at the orphanage"],[12756,12870,"can't manage without me."],[12873,12990,"I really should head back today."],[13153,13353,"Anne, no need to see me off."],[13400,13500,"Don't make me worry about you."],[13543,13650,"But, President..."],[13673,13813,"Wait, President!"],[13856,14136,"Anne, the Sinclair family tells the public"],[14143,14350,"you're an old friend's granddaughter."],[14385,14566,"You're joining the Sinclair Group soon."],[14570,14750,"I don't want a soul to know"],[14759,14874,"you're a nobody."],[14878,15040,"An orphan with no background."],[15286,15516,"President, I'm sorry."]],"12":[[0,63,"Hey, hey."],[73,136,"Look."],[180,276,"Is that our Sinclair Group's"],[280,383,"young master's fiancée?"],[393,520,"She's so pretty."],[520,633,"I heard she's the Chairman's"],[633,750,"old friend's granddaughter."],[782,972,"A wealthy heiress from a prestigious family."],[1003,1106,"So what?"],[1113,1283,"Vice President Sinclair only loves Grace."],[1313,1500,"And Grace majored in Jewelry Design"],[1503,1633,"at a top-tier university."],[1650,1950,"But she only graduated from a lame college."],[2010,2226,"True love and degrees count for nothing."],[2240,2356,"Prominent families only care about"],[2360,2456,"matching social status."],[2496,2593,"Look at her."],[2593,2706,"She started in the Design Department"],[2710,2833,"as the leader of Group Two."],[2833,3050,"There were small issues with this draft."],[3053,3160,"I modified it for you."],[3160,3236,"Take a look."],[3283,3430,"Miss Sinclair, I always felt"],[3433,3590,"this draft wasn't good enough."],[3593,3740,"But I couldn't pinpoint the issue."],[3740,3890,"You fixed it perfectly."],[4096,4286,"Mia, in this document,"],[4290,4403,"there are four errors."],[4403,4530,"I've marked them for you."],[4533,4610,"Take a look."],[4676,4853,"Miss Sinclair, is this really"],[4853,5000,"your first day at work?"],[5010,5133,"You're amazing."],[5133,5170,"Come on."],[5203,5373,"Don't you know who Miss Sinclair is?"],[5423,5570,"She's Mr. Sinclair's fiancée,"],[5573,5726,"the future lady boss of the Sinclair Group."],[5760,5866,"She sure is something."],[5950,6026,"Grace."],[6050,6133,"As soon as Anne arrived,"],[6133,6266,"she stole all your thunder."],[6383,6720,"She's a bast*rd from an orphanage."],[6736,6880,"How dare she steal my thunder?"],[7150,7376,"Anne, I heard from Gavin"],[7376,7500,"the President of the orphanage"],[7503,7670,"where you were born visited recently."],[7700,7877,"Why didn't you show her around the city"],[7880,7980,"for a few more days?"],[7980,8186,"Wait. Isn't Miss Sinclair"],[8190,8373,"a rich heiress?"],[8393,8511,"How could she come from an orphanage?"],[8543,8583,"Oops."],[8600,8683,"Anne,"],[8683,8816,"I guess nobody knew"],[8820,8976,"that you came from an orphanage."],[8980,9106,"I shouldn't have said it."],[9133,9230,"I'm so sorry."],[9760,9836,"Grace Blake."],[9896,9983,"I thought you only"],[9983,10126,"played the victim before men."],[10190,10436,"But you do it with colleagues too."],[10453,10696,"I didn't mean to let that slip."],[10724,10911,"Why are you so mad?"],[10923,11070,"Didn't you hear about it?"],[11073,11206,"In order to marry rich,"],[11210,11320,"some women pretend to be socialites."],[11383,11466,"Miss Sinclair,"],[11470,11586,"you wouldn't be one of them, right?"],[11600,11750,"I know who I am."],[11773,11896,"My engagement is legitimate,"],[12016,12173,"and I'm no homewrecker."]],"13":[[10,220,"Anne's status as an heiress is fake."],[220,363,"She's just an orphan,"],[363,516,"and no one knows who her parents are."],[536,680,"Then why would Mr. Sinclair marry her?"],[680,866,"A psychic said she has a lucky fate."],[873,1050,"The Sinclairs bought her for good luck."],[1110,1273,"So Vice President Sinclair"],[1273,1423,"is just after the inheritance."],[1423,1540,"He has to marry a nobody,"],[1543,1670,"a mascot with no background at all."],[1673,1780,"Looking at it that way,"],[1780,1916,"Mr. Gavin Sinclair is so poor."],[2415,2530,"What are you doing?"],[2533,2756,"I warned you just the other day"],[2790,2923,"to keep your shameful"],[2923,3070,"background well hidden."],[3130,3340,"Are you deaf?"],[3363,3493,"I didn't say it."],[3496,3630,"Grace said it!"],[3660,3843,"Anne, you're the one"],[3843,4006,"who insisted on defending the orphanage."],[4023,4186,"How can you pin this on me?"],[4293,4456,"Anne, since you care so much"],[4460,4623,"about that orphanage,"],[4653,4860,"I'm going to tear it down right now!"],[4943,5193,"Gavin!"],[5213,5298,"Calm down."],[5303,5386,"You can't tear down the orphanage!"],[5453,5530,"Get lost!"],[6144,6296,"Gavin, please, I'm begging you."],[6406,6563,"Anne, you'd rather"],[6566,6753,"beg Gavin so pitifully"],[6800,6946,"than even look at me."],[7036,7113,"We really can't move."],[7116,7223,"There are so many children here."],[7223,7336,"Where are we supposed to go?"],[7340,7473,"You're being unreasonable!"],[7476,7626,"What does that have to do with me?"],[7633,7686,"But..."],[7686,7830,"I told you to move out, so hurry up!"],[7870,8033,"You... You're being unreasonable!"],[8033,8176,"-Grace, what are you doing? -Anne."],[8190,8293,"Anne."],[8303,8406,"About what Gavin said today,"],[8410,8516,"you heard it all, didn't you?"],[8520,8703,"Sinclair Group is reclaiming this land now."],[8703,8840,"You'd better tell them to be sensible"],[8843,8956,"and move out immediately."],[8996,9166,"Or don't blame us if we use force."],[9170,9356,"Sinclair Group said they're reclaiming the land,"],[9363,9506,"but not today."],[9550,9673,"Do you have the demolition order?"],[9673,9856,"The order will be issued tomorrow."],[9876,10060,"I'd advise you not to embarrass yourself."],[10060,10226,"Gavin wants to tear down this orphanage."],[10230,10396,"Right now, aside from his uncle,"],[10403,10526,"who has the power to stop him?"],[10580,10793,"A lowly niece-in-law like you?"],[10800,11070,"His uncle wouldn't even give you a glance."],[11130,11223,"Without a demolition order,"],[11223,11340,"no one touches this place!"],[11383,11486,"If you try to force it,"],[11490,11616,"I'll call the police immediately!"],[11640,11830,"Since you refuse to face reality,"],[11856,11980,"I'll wait one more night."],[12016,12183,"Once I get the order tomorrow,"],[12183,12380,"I'll level this place to the ground."],[12656,12846,"Anne, what do we do?"],[12850,13026,"Nico and Luna are still sick,"],[13033,13163,"and they just got settled here."],[13170,13256,"It's okay. Don't worry."],[13293,13370,"I'm here. I'll handle it."]],"14":[[550,720,"Anne, you're finally here."],[723,906,"I can sing Fireflies now."],[923,1046,"Then sing it for me,"],[1046,1130,"okay?"],[1150,1206,"Okay."],[1242,1396,"♪ Fireflies fly ♪"],[1750,1903,"These children"],[1966,2153,"have already been abandoned once."],[2326,2463,"They finally managed to settle"],[2466,2573,"into this home."],[2686,2917,"I can't let them be cast aside again."],[2954,3010,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[3010,3153,"these are the designs"],[3156,3256,"from our team."],[3256,3345,"I think they're pretty good."],[3346,3440,"Would you like to take a look?"],[4362,4526,"Mr. Sinclair, I'll get back to work then."],[4526,4610,"Close the door."],[4610,4683,"Yes, sir."],[5576,5646,"What is it?"],[5970,6060,"Uncle Arman,"],[6083,6276,"can you stop the orphanage demolition?"],[6323,6440,"There are still over thirty"],[6443,6593,"homeless children inside."],[6656,6756,"Please help them."],[6910,7053,"I'm happy to do charity."],[7166,7270,"But regarding that land,"],[7270,7413,"it was your cheating fiancé"],[7413,7546,"who proposed reclaiming it."],[7575,7730,"He's the company's VP,"],[7770,7883,"so my hands are tied."],[9236,9305,"Uncle Arman,"],[9466,9623,"I know you have a way."],[10313,10416,"Not enough."],[12206,12300,"Change a position."]],"15":[[1843,1930,"Open your eyes."],[2023,2106,"Look at me."],[5523,5606,"You may leave."],[8193,8276,"Uncle Arman,"],[8313,8510,"I'm counting on you to help the orphanage."],[8563,8723,"You're quite confident in yourself, aren't you?"],[8826,8926,"You think sleeping with me"],[8930,9033,"is enough to make me help you?"],[9093,9170,"Yeah."],[9263,9426,"To Arman,"],[9476,9590,"I'm probably just a tool he uses"],[9593,9780,"to humiliate Gavin."],[9903,10140,"Still here? You want me again?"],[10183,10250,"Uncle Arman,"],[10316,10536,"as long as you can save Star Orphanage,"],[10593,10790,"I'll do anything you want."],[10827,10953,"Anything?"],[11086,11285,"What if I tell you not to marry Gavin?"]],"16":[[8,78,"Ugh."],[180,286,"A bunch of b*stards!"],[286,393,"You don't wanna leave?"],[420,495,"Grace!"],[497,620,"Don't waste time on them."],[636,785,"Just throw these little brats out."],[786,893,"Don't hurt my children!"],[893,1040,"Listen, old hag."],[1040,1196,"I heard Anne cares about you a lot."],[1200,1406,"Then let me take care of you."],[1432,1473,"Ah!"],[1474,1620,"Don't hit Mom!"],[1620,1736,"Stop!"],[1736,1836,"Mom!"],[1890,1973,"Let me go!"],[2023,2120,"What are you doing?!"],[2352,2443,"What?"],[2486,2643,"Who gave you the right to hit people?!"],[2643,2770,"This is the Sinclair family's land."],[2773,2920,"And the Sinclair family's land is Gavin's."],[2920,3076,"I can do whatever I want."],[3076,3226,"Exactly. The Sinclair family's assets"],[3226,3370,"will belong to my daughter in the future."],[3376,3523,"Grace, aren't you afraid"],[3523,3748,"I'll tell Sir Sinclair about you and Gavin?"],[3750,3860,"So what if you do?"],[3886,4056,"I'm pregnant with Gavin's child."],[4060,4183,"I'm dying for you to tell him."],[4183,4326,"I don't believe Sir Sinclair"],[4326,4466,"would turn away his own great-grandson."],[4470,4563,"You're pregnant?"],[4576,4703,"My daughter is carrying"],[4703,4873,"Sir Sinclair's first great-grandson."],[4873,4926,"Haha."],[4943,5100,"To reward me, Gavin gave"],[5106,5380,"the new Sinclair Group's project to my dad."],[5400,5656,"The Sinclair family's assets will be mine."],[5673,5986,"Throw away these b*stards and stuff!"],[5989,6099,"Don't leave a single thing."],[6101,6180,"Stop!"],[6220,6350,"Grace, you're about to"],[6350,6446,"become a mother yourself."],[6446,6600,"Aren't you afraid of karma?"],[6600,6683,"Karma?"],[6716,6873,"I don't believe in karma."],[6873,6970,"I only believe in fate."],[7016,7146,"A bi*ch like you"],[7163,7306,"deserves to be trampled on."],[7346,7480,"These kids are too loud."],[7480,7633,"Tape their mouths shut."],[7733,7806,"No!"],[7806,7956,"No, please don't!"],[7956,8056,"Know your place,"],[8056,8193,"or I'll throw you out, too."],[8205,8272,"Stop!"],[8930,8983,"Dad."],[9300,9433,"Who do you think you are?"],[9458,9640,"How dare you lay a hand on my family?"]],"17":[[32,155,"Who the hell are you?"],[159,282,"Do you know who I am?"],[293,463,"Dad, this is Gavin's uncle."],[466,543,"Mr. Sinclair."],[600,763,"Uncle Arman, why are you here?"],[826,950,"If I hadn't come, how would I know"],[950,1100,"you were messing with the Sinclair family?"],[1263,1406,"Oh, it's Gavin's uncle."],[1410,1503,"We're all family here."],[1503,1646,"Family?"],[1684,1894,"Has Gavin really stooped so low?"],[1920,2030,"An a*shole like you"],[2030,2226,"can claim to be the Sinclairs' family?"],[2230,2313,"Uncle Arman,"],[2316,2500,"Anne led those orphans"],[2503,2660,"to stop us reclaiming the Sinclairs' land."],[2670,2890,"I had no choice but to stop her."],[2893,3046,"Grace, it was you!"],[3050,3226,"You didn't give President Adams any time."],[3290,3406,"You ordered an immediate demolition."],[3420,3616,"Where can they move on such short notice?"],[3620,3806,"Uncle Arman, you heard that?"],[3813,3920,"Anne is doing this only because"],[3923,4026,"she was born in this orphanage."],[4030,4136,"She's siding with them"],[4176,4350,"to block Sinclair Group's development."],[4388,4586,"I don't recall having a niece like you."],[4680,4806,"Call me Mr. Sinclair!"],[4870,5016,"Since Anne opposes the demolition,"],[5062,5166,"then let's not demolish it."],[5233,5466,"Mr. Sinclair, but the board approved it."],[5493,5620,"The plans are already drawn up."],[5643,5830,"Then tell them to pick a new site"],[5846,5983,"and make new plans."],[6013,6170,"If anyone on the board has objections,"],[6173,6306,"tell them to talk to me!"],[6346,6507,"I have ways to kick them off the board!"],[6533,6596,"But..."],[6646,6722,"Guards!"],[6873,7020,"Pull up the surveillance footage."],[7080,7213,"Anyone who hit President Adams"],[7213,7363,"and the children..."],[7373,7486,"Don't let them off!"],[7490,7712,"Mr. Sinclair, my Dad did it for Sinclair Group!"],[7716,7813,"That's right, Mr. Sinclair."],[7813,7943,"I... I did it for Sinclair Group."],[7946,8197,"Besides, Grace is carrying Gavin's child."],[8206,8336,"I'm the child's grandfather!"],[8340,8566,"She's carrying Gavin's b*stard."],[8583,8733,"What does that have to do with me?"],[8780,8830,"You..."],[8830,8953,"Take them away!"],[8953,9120,"Mr. Sinclair, my Dad only works for"],[9123,9243,"Sinclair Group!"],[9360,9530,"If you weren't still useful,"],[9540,9676,"I'd put you in jail, too."],[9683,9833,"Why would Arman help"],[9833,10062,"a lowly niece-in-law like Anne?"],[10146,10244,"Get lost!"],[10953,11103,"Are you satisfied with this result?"],[11283,11456,"Thank you, Uncle Arman."],[11474,11616,"I don't like verbal thanks."],[12120,12256,"Mom."]],"18":[[256,393,"President, you're awake."],[770,820,"Ugh."],[866,1176,"Anne, I made you worry."],[1300,1400,"As long as you're okay."],[1400,1540,"How are the children?"],[1540,1753,"Don't worry, they're all settled."],[1753,2060,"Anne, Gavin treats you so poorly."],[2061,2240,"Why didn't you tell me sooner?"],[2280,2466,"My bad."],[2636,2776,"Please don't say that."],[2776,2913,"Except for Gavin,"],[2916,3070,"my life in the Sinclair family"],[3073,3196,"is actually going quite well."],[3210,3341,"But you still have a long life"],[3342,3460,"ahead of you."],[3473,3550,"It's fine."],[3597,3870,"Besides, Gavin used to really love me."],[3870,4113,"I believe once he's had his fun,"],[4113,4386,"he'll settle down and come back to me."],[4413,4546,"Gavin treats you like that,"],[4553,4736,"yet you're still so devoted to him."],[4798,5055,"We owe it all to Uncle Arman this time."],[5136,5433,"Make sure you thank him properly."],[5693,5756,"Right."],[5813,5920,"Where is Uncle Arman?"],[6960,7126,"Thank you for today."],[7586,7720,"Go thank Gavin instead."],[9570,9640,"Anne Sinclair!"],[9640,9806,"How dare you team up with Arman"],[9806,9940,"to bully Grace?"],[9943,10030,"Gavin Sinclair!"],[10090,10182,"What about you?"],[10182,10403,"You teamed up with Grace to bully me"],[10403,10553,"and the people I care about."],[10574,10721,"Who do you think you are?"],[10753,10900,"How dare you challenge me?"],[10906,10990,"Also,"],[11022,11232,"why did Arman stand up for you?"],[11233,11363,"Did you sleep with him?"],[11411,11622,"Enough! You saved my life."],[11743,12006,"So I've put up with everything for years."],[12009,12106,"You cheated on me,"],[12186,12246,"and I endured it."],[12246,12353,"And now?"],[12376,12592,"Am I supposed to accept Grace's child too?"],[12713,12900,"How do you know Grace is pregnant?"],[13076,13200,"Go ask her yourself."],[13340,13420,"Gavin,"],[13476,13630,"I'll still marry you."],[13724,13886,"But from now on,"],[14036,14210,"don't ever think you can control me."]],"19":[[166,350,"Gavin, the lawyer said"],[350,470,"my dad is definitely going to jail."],[470,583,"Stop crying."],[593,673,"Let me ask you."],[686,820,"Did you tell Anne"],[820,920,"you're pregnant?"],[920,1096,"She was about to hit me,"],[1110,1253,"and I was so scared."],[1253,1420,"So I used the baby to protect myself."],[1420,1603,"My dad was arrested by the police."],[1613,1780,"If I didn't have this baby,"],[1780,1940,"I would be in there too."],[1940,2113,"It's all Anne's fault."],[2543,2866,"Gavin, why did Uncle Arman take Anne's side?"],[2893,3080,"Is she cheating on you with Arman?"],[3080,3323,"No way. She loves me."],[3333,3533,"I just need to coax her a little."],[3560,3803,"Arman has been provoking me since he got back."],[3810,3943,"He even went to the orphanage today"],[3943,4090,"to back up Anne."],[4163,4350,"I really have to watch out for him."],[5126,5286,"To him, something like this"],[5340,5516,"probably means nothing."],[6394,6474,"Anne,"],[6620,6856,"I've realized that I can't live without you."],[8453,8636,"Uncle Arman, you..."],[8750,8936,"If you want to expose our relationship,"],[9066,9140,"then go ahead and scream."],[9666,9783,"What are you doing?"],[10126,10350,"I don't want you to marry Gavin."],[11140,11250,"You're drunk."],[11286,11430,"Let me help you to your room."],[12123,12216,"Uncle Arman,"],[12266,12386,"we're at home."],[12470,12560,"Let go of me."],[13280,13360,"Uncle Arman!"],[15278,15383,"Anne."],[15450,15596,"You asked for this."]],"20":[[330,456,"I can't believe Arman actually"],[456,653,"slept in my room last night."],[1640,1716,"Good morning."],[1893,1973,"Uncle Arman,"],[2030,2230,"why didn't you go back last night?"],[2230,2483,"I was too tired to leave last night."],[2496,2626,"What?"],[2792,2999,"Then... then you need to leave now."],[3040,3113,"Hurry up and go."],[3150,3373,"Hurry. Someone might come."],[3453,3556,"Just go."],[3633,3716,"Fine."],[3898,3990,"Anne,"],[4020,4093,"are you awake?"],[4100,4273,"Let's go to the office together."],[4386,4616,"Do you want me to leave"],[4640,4836,"or do you want me to stay?"],[5016,5173,"Hide somewhere first!"],[5182,5286,"Leave later!"],[5313,5406,"Quick!"],[5503,5633,"Hurry."],[5726,5830,"I'm begging you."],[6246,6463,"Why are you still here? Hurry up!"],[6703,6846,"Weird."],[6846,7010,"Mr. Sinclair is usually up by now."],[7807,7893,"Anne."],[7910,8026,"Anne, what are you doing?"]],"21":[[1066,1176,"What's wrong, Gavin?"],[1216,1336,"What are you looking for?"],[1336,1520,"Is Arman in your room?"],[1520,1653,"What are you talking about?"],[1656,1830,"How could Uncle Arman be in my room?"],[1830,1973,"Then why did you lock the door?"],[1983,2176,"I was about to take a shower."],[2876,2986,"What's wrong with you?"],[3260,3430,"You'd better behave yourself."],[3434,3586,"Get changed and come out."],[3610,3746,"I'll wait for you at the door."],[4426,4497,"Grandpa."],[4499,4546,"Oh."],[4550,4616,"Anne,"],[4636,4773,"look at your Uncle Arman."],[4792,4936,"He is unbelievable."],[4960,5143,"Still in bed at this hour."],[5166,5326,"I heard last night,"],[5326,5503,"he got drunk at a nightclub."],[5523,5636,"No wonder he can't get up."],[5650,5716,"Are you spreading rumors"],[5720,5826,"just because I'm not around?"],[6030,6130,"Last night, I was drinking alone"],[6130,6243,"in my car."],[6330,6360,"Oh."],[6406,6528,"What happened to your foot?"],[6531,6693,"I snuck over to my girlfriend's last night,"],[6710,6856,"but her boyfriend showed up unexpectedly."],[6880,7150,"I twisted my ankle jumping out the window."],[7156,7343,"He won't stop"],[7345,7492,"until he gets me killed."],[7499,7630,"I told you a long time ago!"],[7630,7900,"Cut ties with those shady women!"],[7944,8074,"But you just won't listen, will you?"],[8084,8190,"And I told you."],[8196,8313,"I love her."],[8313,8386,"You..."],[8498,8643,"You pissed me off!"]],"22":[[3,116,"Grandpa, calm down."],[116,211,"Alright, that's enough."],[616,833,"Uncle Arman, considering our family's status,"],[836,1031,"how can you go be a homewrecker?"],[1280,1566,"You'd better find a decent wife."],[1653,1830,"Your own engagement is falling apart."],[1863,1986,"Worry about yourself first."],[2090,2220,"My relationship with Anne"],[2220,2310,"is very stable."],[2383,2580,"We're going to the office together later."],[2656,2820,"Oh? You don't mind"],[2823,2940,"she's from the orphanage today?"],[2940,3063,"Aren't you going to tear down the orphanage?"],[3243,3400,"Uncle Arman, about yesterday,"],[3490,3623,"thank you for stepping in"],[3633,3756,"and fixing my mistake."],[3796,3900,"But from now on,"],[3900,4040,"when it comes to our affairs,"],[4040,4166,"don't interfere."],[4273,4510,"Let's see a movie after work tonight."],[4893,5030,"When I helped you yesterday,"],[5033,5183,"you said you owed me a favor."],[5243,5353,"My ankle is twisted today,"],[5356,5450,"so I can't drive."],[5513,5610,"Uncle Arman,"],[5660,5857,"Anne is a terrible driver."],[5896,6000,"I'll help you instead."],[6036,6150,"I'm a clean freak."],[6200,6300,"I don't like others touching my car."],[6650,6756,"Don't keep me waiting too long."],[7333,7466,"You're not allowed to drive for him."],[7516,7730,"Gavin, if Grace hadn't"],[7733,7916,"pushed me so hard yesterday,"],[7940,8173,"I wouldn't have asked Uncle Arman for help."],[8210,8303,"Try to understand."],[8346,8447,"I'll go get my bag."]],"23":[[1126,1206,"Get in."],[3486,3556,"Uncle Arman, don't."],[3589,3660,"Gavin is coming."],[4316,4434,"What are you doing?"],[4492,4590,"Why haven't you left yet?"],[6708,6800,"Arman,"],[6833,6946,"just you wait."]],"24":[[513,706,"No physical contact with Gavin from now on."],[1033,1270,"Is he jealous?"],[1810,1890,"Hello?"],[1993,2186,"Miss, the Design Department has a meeting."],[2200,2407,"The proposal for the jewelry exhibition entry,"],[2410,2503,"did you bring it?"],[2540,2660,"Yes, I have it."],[2710,2843,"Okay, see you then."],[3790,3870,"Hello."],[3890,3970,"Check out."],[3986,4103,"One minute, please."],[4580,4660,"Hello?"],[4703,4916,"Miss Sinclair gave up the chance to go abroad."],[4953,5086,"She didn't even attend Capital University."],[5146,5397,"She chose a design major in Seaside City."],[5560,5656,"Anne,"],[5660,5810,"what kind of spell does Gavin cast on you?"],[5833,6003,"You even gave up on your dreams."],[6200,6313,"You love design so much."],[6423,6580,"Why didn't you go to Capital University?"],[6630,6840,"I wasn't good enough."],[6900,7070,"Besides, it's not like"],[7070,7223,"I could just go if I wanted to."]],"25":[[630,790,"Miss, I saw your design draft."],[790,863,"It's amazing."],[863,943,"Not at all."],[943,1080,"There's still a lot to improve."],[1080,1190,"Stop being so modest."],[1190,1293,"We all saw it."],[1293,1406,"It's incredibly impressive."],[1406,1543,"Yeah, we saw it."],[1543,1623,"You're really good."],[1703,1893,"Anne's design draft is so good."],[1963,2063,"I absolutely cannot let her"],[2063,2156,"participate in the jewelry exhibition."],[2353,2440,"Grace."],[2496,2660,"What's wrong? Why are you zoning out?"],[3203,3283,"Gavin."],[3303,3410,"I just saw your Uncle Arman"],[3410,3553,"arrive with Anne."],[3583,3753,"They've actually teamed up?"],[3753,3883,"Relax."],[3883,4090,"Anne is just a dog I raised."],[4123,4380,"I won't let her escape my grasp."],[4410,4526,"You should be careful."],[4583,4720,"If she gains some real power,"],[4720,4806,"what if she tries to break free?"],[4806,4970,"She graduated from a lame college."],[4970,5146,"What skills could she possibly have?"],[5146,5320,"But if her work"],[5320,5480,"makes a name for itself at the exhibition,"],[5486,5603,"then things will be different."],[5613,5916,"However, she does have some talent in design."],[5930,6013,"This jewelry exhibition"],[6013,6140,"BC Group is participating, too."],[6153,6263,"It's going to be a global sensation."],[6300,6463,"I've seen Anne's design draft."],[6486,6610,"If she competes,"],[6620,6723,"she'll definitely outshine me."],[6780,6996,"Don't worry, I won't let her"],[7000,7143,"get that chance."],[7180,7270,"When the time comes,"],[7270,7403,"get her design drafts to me."],[7440,7586,"Leave the rest to me."]],"26":[[53,253,"Team leader, why does the VP"],[253,330,"make us assist the Grace Team"],[333,436,"with their work?"],[466,633,"We even have to fetch dinner for them?"],[723,900,"It's fine. Just a small thing."],[1556,1633,"Uncle..."],[1946,2036,"Mr. Sinclair."],[2448,2582,"When did you transfer to Logistics?"],[2854,3000,"I'm still new to the company"],[3000,3116,"and lack experience."],[3130,3300,"Learning from other teams"],[3303,3410,"helps me gain experience."],[3466,3620,"Mr. Sinclair, our Team Leader"],[3623,3750,"is clearly very talented."],[3753,3850,"Her designs are unique"],[3853,3950,"and simply stunning."],[3980,4110,"If the VP wasn't so biased,"],[4110,4246,"how could her work..."],[4247,4310,"Mia."],[4353,4420,"Enough."],[4456,4540,"Stop talking."],[4543,4690,"You listen to Gavin so much."],[4726,4796,"If Gavin asked you to jump into a river,"],[4800,4863,"would you do it?"],[5190,5363,"I was a swimming champion."],[5773,5860,"He's the Vice President,"],[5863,5945,"and I'm his employee."],[5947,6106,"I have to listen to him."],[6143,6226,"Then I'll go find him."],[6293,6330,"Hey."],[6330,6400,"Uncle..."]],"27":[[638,712,"Let go..."],[848,964,"Let go of me."],[1130,1233,"Come find me after you drop that off."],[1363,1463,"Okay."],[2370,2460,"I'm sending you a design."],[2460,2653,"Enter it in the exhibition under BC Group."],[2690,2770,"Understood."],[2783,2900,"Who's the designer?"],[2936,3033,"Anne Sinclair."],[3090,3283,"You want to submit Miss Sinclair's work"],[3290,3473,"on behalf of our company?"],[3563,3670,"The Sinclair Group doesn't deserve her."],[4326,4413,"Where is she?"],[5493,5580,"That concludes the design concept"],[5580,5713,"for my piece."],[5940,6043,"Manager Blake, your design"],[6043,6206,"is truly stunning."],[6216,6406,"This piece will surely shine"],[6406,6580,"at the jewelry exhibition."],[7213,7510,"Grace, this is theft!"],[7513,7600,"What's going on?"],[7606,7833,"Didn't Miss Blake draw the design?"],[7893,8003,"I spent half a year"],[8003,8173,"creating this piece."],[8266,8456,"How dare you!"]],"28":[[23,120,"Anne,"],[132,323,"if you have a problem with me, just say it."],[326,508,"But don't insult my professional integrity."],[513,718,"I spent months slaving over this design."],[720,843,"How did it suddenly become yours?"],[843,960,"What exactly is going on here?"],[1153,1230,"Everyone,"],[1306,1453,"this piece is called Heartsea."],[1470,1573,"I designed it six months ago"],[1576,1756,"specifically for this jewelry exhibition."],[1853,2043,"Grace asked me for it this morning."],[2046,2153,"I refused."],[2186,2392,"She stole it while I wasn't looking."],[2423,2540,"I didn't steal anything!"],[2563,2680,"This is my design!"],[2813,2963,"Anne, haven't you caused enough trouble?"],[2966,3080,"You're my fiancée."],[3083,3176,"I know exactly"],[3176,3336,"what you're capable of."],[3343,3460,"If you can't come up with a good design,"],[3460,3586,"I won't blame you."],[3603,3780,"But you can't rely on your status"],[3781,3904,"to steal from others."],[3933,4030,"So you're trying to use your position"],[4033,4216,"to take credit for someone else's work."],[4220,4426,"Thank God Vice President Sinclair is fair."],[4450,4586,"I've heard people from orphanages"],[4590,4703,"have sticky fingers."],[4706,4876,"I thought it was just petty theft."],[4896,4987,"I didn't expect she'd try to snatch"],[4987,5084,"others' design draft."],[5123,5240,"Shameless."],[5460,5583,"Say that again!"],[5640,5726,"Miss Sinclair,"],[5733,5926,"we regular employees also have dignity."],[5933,6090,"What gives you the right to hit me?"],[6103,6223,"She really is from an orphanage."],[6223,6316,"No class at all."],[6330,6406,"Exactly!"],[6450,6530,"This piece!"],[6530,6683,"From the start of the design until now,"],[6686,6793,"the sketches I've piled up"],[6793,6906,"are over a foot and a half high."],[6986,7103,"And the design concepts..."],[7113,7258,"I can show everyone all the proof right now."],[7263,7333,"Enough!"],[7573,7703,"Anne, everything you have"],[7706,7810,"belongs to the Sinclair family."],[7863,8016,"Even your life belongs to me."],[8023,8150,"Don't you dare make a scene."],[8580,8676,"Fine."],[8740,8963,"Gavin, this design..."],[9020,9133,"I'm giving it to Grace."],[9183,9376,"But the debt for saving my life is paid."],[9590,9666,"I don't owe you anymore."]],"29":[[26,133,"I quit."],[180,283,"Don't you dare!"],[8080,8236,"I didn't go home again last night."],[10293,10520,"Anne, where the hell were you?"],[10533,10686,"Were you with Arman?"]],"30":[[270,476,"U-Uncle Arman..."],[570,683,"Last night, I..."],[723,756,"I..."],[760,873,"What are you shy about?"],[913,1043,"It's not like it's our first night together."],[1090,1273,"J-Just give me my bra first."],[1384,1596,"But I think you look better without one."],[2110,2173,"Alright."],[2213,2413,"Get ready and come eat."],[3734,3820,"Come eat."],[3825,3895,"Mhm."],[4206,4269,"Try it."],[4277,4440,"Tomato egg noodles."],[4502,4616,"My favorite."],[4642,4735,"Did you make this?"],[4963,5030,"Who else?"],[5059,5258,"You think I only wanna have sex with you?"],[6523,6590,"Eat up."],[6660,6786,"Waiting for me to feed you?"],[6916,7026,"With your mouth?"],[9275,9398,"With my mouth?"],[9741,9914,"I-I was wrong."]],"31":[[316,403,"Ahem."],[750,833,"Hello?"],[906,990,"Is this Anne Sinclair?"],[1066,1133,"Yes."],[1163,1230,"We really like"],[1233,1333,"the work you submitted."],[1353,1480,"We'd like to ask when you can"],[1483,1606,"start working with our group?"],[1696,1800,"BC Group?"],[2083,2170,"I never submitted"],[2173,2293,"any work to you."],[2296,2406,"Besides, \"Heartsea\""],[2410,2523,"is already with Sinclair Group."],[2580,2756,"I won't be working for you."],[2856,2923,"Miss Sinclair,"],[2976,3140,"don't be so quick to say no."],[3143,3233,"Think it over."],[3233,3326,"BC Group's doors"],[3330,3466,"are always open to you."],[3806,3990,"Uncle Arman, I really didn't"],[3990,4133,"submit anything to BC Group."],[4303,4410,"I don't care."],[4460,4610,"If you want to work at BC Group,"],[4636,4788,"I can drive you there right now."],[4816,4910,"That wouldn't be appropriate."],[4983,5200,"Sinclair Group and BC Group are sworn enemies."],[5456,5603,"Following your heart"],[5630,5716,"is more important."],[6020,6156,"I think I might"],[6203,6320,"still want to go back"],[6323,6476,"and perfect \"Heartsea\"."],[6520,6716,"After that, I'll probably"],[6720,6866,"just leave Sinclair Group."],[7000,7186,"Did Gavin save your life or something?"],[7216,7386,"Why are you so devoted to him?"],[7476,7590,"You don't know?"],[7654,7753,"Know what?"],[7863,8020,"Actually, Gavin"],[8233,8336,"Wait a sec."],[8880,9110,"The Future Young Mistress of Sinclair Group..."],[9113,9186,"Abusing her status"],[9186,9323,"to openly steal credit"],[9353,9496,"and bully coworkers,"],[9523,9656,"as confirmed by Sinclair Group's VP,"],[9660,9786,"Gavin."],[9810,9923,"Anne has now been"],[9923,10046,"blacklisted from the industry."],[10493,10553,"No."],[11550,11636,"Gavin,"],[11716,11860,"I already gave her the design."],[11950,12060,"Why are you still slandering"],[12060,12163,"and smearing my name?"],[12200,12306,"This is your punishment"],[12323,12420,"for not answering my calls,"],[12423,12536,"ignoring my messages,"],[12603,12756,"and defying me."]],"32":[[16,100,"Fine."],[196,323,"Then I'll expose the fact"],[326,450,"that you stole my designs"],[453,536,"to everyone."],[613,690,"Anne,"],[773,1026,"with me, your fiancé, testifying,"],[1030,1220,"who would believe you now?"],[1260,1453,"Gavin, Anne is still"],[1453,1583,"your fiancée, after all."],[1620,1743,"Don't be so harsh on her."],[1776,1930,"Just give her another chance."],[1996,2060,"Fine."],[2100,2243,"Since Grace is pleading for you,"],[2246,2443,"I'll give you another chance."],[2470,2683,"As long as you admit to the company"],[2683,2823,"that you tried to steal Grace's work,"],[2867,2980,"I'll let you return to Sinclair Group"],[2983,3100,"and keep your job."],[3140,3266,"But from now on, you'll only"],[3270,3476,"design pieces for Grace."],[3583,3820,"You stole my work,"],[3943,4080,"and framing me wasn't enough?"],[4083,4180,"Now you want me to keep"],[4183,4326,"designing for you?"],[4343,4536,"Where do you get the nerve?"],[4700,4736,"Anne,"],[4740,4853,"think clearly."],[4953,5176,"If you don't cherish this opportunity,"],[5176,5313,"your career as a designer"],[5313,5486,"ends right here!"],[5563,5680,"That's right, Anne."],[5693,5856,"We're giving you a chance."],[5950,6116,"Even if I never"],[6116,6250,"step foot in the industry again,"],[6363,6500,"don't expect me to be"],[6503,6643,"your puppet."],[6793,6933,"You're just an orphan."],[6980,7116,"To the Sinclair family, you're just a"],[7116,7223,"mascot."],[7223,7346,"You're just a f*cking mascot."],[7350,7446,"What reputation?"],[7753,7846,"Gavin,"],[7846,8086,"I'm claiming this reputation."],[8153,8240,"Anne,"],[8243,8403,"how could you hit Gavin?"],[8583,8660,"Anne."],[8760,8933,"Those orphans at the orphanage are all"],[8933,9113,"supported by the Sinclair family."],[9170,9306,"You'd better believe I can make them"],[9306,9480,"starve to death in minutes!"]],"33":[[180,300,"That's right, Anne."],[320,473,"Gavin has a point."],[480,663,"You were bought by the Sinclairs anyway,"],[676,793,"so why bother with saving face?"],[796,960,"Survival is what matters."],[1343,1626,"Fine. Just wait and see."],[1993,2070,"Gavin,"],[2130,2366,"Anne won't go running her mouth, will she?"],[2443,2693,"Relax. With me as a witness,"],[2696,2863,"who would believe her?"],[2903,3186,"Being a designer is her lifelong dream."],[3213,3443,"Now that she's blacklisted in the industry,"],[3443,3620,"not even small workshops will hire her."],[3730,3873,"Before long,"],[3873,4066,"she'll come back begging us."],[4083,4300,"But what if Uncle Arman helps her again?"],[4536,4656,"Arman is only"],[4660,4843,"tough within the Sinclair family."],[4873,5026,"He relies on Grandpa's favoritism."],[5030,5120,"Right now at Sinclair Group,"],[5120,5326,"he doesn't call the shots alone."],[5330,5556,"As for the outside world, who respects him?"],[5622,5669,"Mm."],[5720,5803,"You're right."],[5856,6013,"As long as you win an award"],[6013,6160,"at this jewelry exhibition,"],[6173,6310,"I'll get the credit,"],[6323,6593,"and I can crush him beneath my feet."]],"34":[[940,1020,"Anne,"],[1120,1236,"you have outstanding ability."],[1253,1440,"Are you willing to be stepped on like this,"],[1470,1596,"never to make a comeback?"],[1616,1783,"Only if you become strong yourself"],[1820,1996,"can you and the children at the orphanage"],[2056,2203,"be free from their control forever."],[2256,2410,"I never believe in karma."],[2430,2520,"I only believe in fate."],[2573,2723,"A cheap life like yours"],[2723,2843,"deserves to be trampled on."],[3170,3273,"I've made up my mind."],[3276,3406,"I will use my designs"],[3407,3563,"to represent BC Group in the exhibition."],[3603,3793,"I'll go report to their company."],[4038,4220,"Congratulations, Anne."],[4250,4396,"You've finally taken a step"],[4410,4540,"toward your life's dream."],[4826,4937,"Miss Sinclair,"],[4973,5046,"hello."],[5046,5300,"Are you Mr. Keane, the VP of BC Group?"],[5300,5506,"It's an honor to welcome Miss Sinclair to BC."],[5540,5620,"Ah!"],[5803,5870,"Ah!"],[5870,5990,"Who is this?"],[6006,6053,"Th—"],[6056,6153,"I'm her boyfriend."],[6233,6323,"I dropped her off."],[6543,6853,"Boss, you're really being brazen."],[6950,7190,"No, this is my Uncle Arman."],[7206,7320,"He's joking."],[7350,7423,"Uncle Arman,"],[7430,7563,"thanks for bringing me here."],[7563,7666,"You should go back now."],[7670,7826,"I'll show you around their company."],[7880,8016,"Perhaps your Uncle Arman is worried"],[8018,8130,"about your working environment here,"],[8136,8250,"and wants to check it out."],[8460,8543,"Let's go."],[8543,8616,"Please."],[8623,8713,"Thank you for the trouble."],[8786,8866,"Miss Sinclair,"],[8900,9028,"we'll assign a team to assist you"],[9033,9216,"in completing Heartsea."],[9253,9357,"Thank you, Mr. Keane."],[9360,9460,"By the way,"],[9460,9563,"I wanted to ask,"],[9563,9673,"who registered me"],[9673,9860,"for the jewelry exhibition?"],[9913,9983,"Uh,"],[10080,10143,"well,"],[10143,10270,"we just saw the name on the entry"],[10270,10403,"was yours, Miss Sinclair,"],[10403,10526,"so we assumed you submitted it yourself."],[10526,10626,"I see."],[10846,10970,"Who could it be?"],[10990,11100,"Who"],[11250,11386,"Our conference room is up ahead."],[11386,11483,"Let me show you around."],[11700,11883,"As a member of the Sinclair family,"],[11883,12110,"instead of stopping me from betraying them,"],[12176,12296,"he actually seems eager"],[12296,12443,"to push me into BC Group."]],"35":[[333,393,"Miss Blake,"],[393,513,"this fur coat is gorgeous."],[513,610,"Where did you get it?"],[623,750,"I brought it back from Hong Kong."],[750,830,"When you accept the award later,"],[830,940,"you'll have such a commanding presence."],[1173,1286,"Anne,"],[1286,1446,"aren't you blacklisted from the industry?"],[1446,1546,"How did you even get in?"],[1546,1670,"I got in on my own merit."],[1690,1830,"Long time no see, Anne."],[1830,1926,"Gavin told me"],[1926,2050,"you've been running around all day"],[2050,2163,"looking for a job."],[2163,2263,"Did you find anything?"],[2280,2470,"I'm well-connected in this industry,"],[2470,2613,"and I haven't heard of anyone hiring her."],[2613,2813,"Don't say that, Maggie."],[2823,2900,"Anne probably found"],[2903,3026,"a related position"],[3026,3186,"at some jewelry company."],[3233,3373,"It's all right, Anne."],[3373,3493,"As long as you admit your mistakes"],[3493,3586,"and work honestly,"],[3586,3773,"you'll surely get another chance."],[3786,3866,"Enough."],[3933,4066,"Gavin isn't here,"],[4066,4206,"so spare me the show."],[4230,4360,"I don't buy your innocent act."],[4480,4560,"Ignore her."],[4680,4763,"Miss Blake,"],[4773,4900,"I heard your entry today"],[4900,4980,"took six months to create."],[4980,5063,"The whole Sinclair executive team"],[5063,5140,"has high hopes for you."],[5143,5266,"This competition piece,"],[5290,5416,"\"Heartsea,\" indeed,"],[5416,5590,"took a great deal of effort to make."],[5600,5673,"I personally believe"],[5673,5730,"that this is my step into"],[5730,5836,"Since I became a designer,"],[5843,5973,"this is the piece I'm most proud of."],[5973,6093,"Let me congratulate you in advance"],[6093,6246,"on taking first place at this exhibition."],[6246,6326,"Thank you."],[6526,6653,"Thank you for your patience."],[6653,6753,"The evaluation results for this exhibition"],[6753,6960,"are finally in."],[6960,7113,"Please give a round of applause"],[7113,7213,"for our panel of judges."],[7993,8106,"Mr. Sinclair and Vice President Sinclair"],[8106,8220,"are both on the panel."],[8260,8406,"That makes our victory a sure thing."],[8500,8596,"Anne,"],[8596,8746,"you'd better leave now."],[8753,8846,"Otherwise, when Miss Blake"],[8846,8950,"goes up to receive the award,"],[8950,9046,"you'll be crying with envy,"],[9046,9180,"and no one will be there to wipe your tears."],[9186,9353,"Don't say that, Maggie."],[9373,9543,"Let Miss Sinclair stay"],[9546,9726,"and admire the work"],[9726,9846,"I spent six months creating."],[9966,10046,"All right."],[10096,10206,"I look forward to it."]],"36":[[3,100,"For the first-prize winning piece"],[103,243,"of this jewelry exhibition,"],[260,366,"please look at the big screen."],[386,493,"Why is the color slightly different"],[496,633,"from my design draft?"],[660,776,"Maybe"],[780,966,"Vice President Sinclair adjusted it later."],[1006,1200,"This color scheme is indeed more vivid"],[1203,1286,"and even more stunning."],[1353,1426,"I'm certain."],[1713,1900,"When Heartsea was finalized,"],[1903,2106,"the diamonds weren't this color."],[2163,2403,"When did Grace change the color scheme?"],[2506,2636,"Now, I will announce"],[2640,2846,"the winner of this jewelry competition."],[3753,3926,"Thank you, thank you, everyone."],[3933,4010,"Miss Sinclair,"],[4030,4073,"as the winner"],[4076,4230,"of this jewelry competition,"],[4230,4333,"do you have any words"],[4333,4470,"to share with everyone?"],[4500,4663,"I am a designer for Sinclair Group,"],[4670,4773,"but my surname isn't Sinclair."],[4773,4863,"My name is Grace."],[4960,5053,"Grace?"],[5086,5283,"But the designer's name on this work"],[5286,5420,"is Anne."],[5663,5760,"Anne."],[6286,6393,"Did you hear that?"],[6393,6656,"The owner of this work is me."]],"37":[[73,216,"Are you Anne?"],[220,300,"This piece,"],[303,483,"took me seven months to complete."],[493,613,"At the bottom,"],[613,716,"you'll find my signature,"],[720,850,"my initials."],[903,1016,"Miss Blake,"],[1043,1120,"how can you claim"],[1123,1300,"that this work is yours?"],[1325,1501,"What is going on?"],[1503,1586,"What's happening?"],[1586,1660,"What is this about?"],[1663,1766,"But the entry I submitted"],[1770,1883,"was Heartsea."],[1883,2062,"This piece is identical to mine."],[2076,2193,"Everyone at Sinclair Group"],[2196,2323,"can testify for me."],[2330,2433,"I can testify."],[2433,2576,"This is Miss Blake's work."],[2576,2663,"She poured her heart into this piece,"],[2663,2786,"working day and night."],[2790,2936,"We all saw it."],[3016,3090,"Miss Blake,"],[3116,3250,"is this your work?"],[3303,3480,"Apart from the colors,"],[3490,3633,"these two pieces are identical."],[3636,3810,"One of them must be a copy."],[3810,3890,"Anne,"],[3916,4056,"I didn't expect that after stealing my work"],[4060,4180,"and getting fired from the company,"],[4180,4273,"you still wouldn't give up."],[4300,4446,"How dare you plagiarize right here?"],[4450,4653,"Is she the one from recently,"],[4653,4806,"exposed for abusing her status to bully staff,"],[4810,5033,"the fiancée of Sinclair Group's VP?"],[5036,5100,"Yes."],[5130,5360,"She was fired for stealing Miss Blake's work"],[5383,5616,"and blacklisted from the industry."],[5670,5748,"It is her."],[5748,5823,"So shameless."],[5823,5953,"Since everyone claims"],[5956,6143,"these two pieces are identical,"],[6143,6280,"yet my piece,"],[6283,6476,"whether in terms of design"],[6500,6706,"or the luster of the gems,"],[6736,6933,"seems superior to Miss Blake's,"],[6963,7146,"so couldn't it be Miss Blake"],[7150,7333,"who copied me?"]],"38":[[3,90,"Anne,"],[133,226,"Mr. Sinclair and Vice President Sinclair"],[230,356,"can both testify for me."],[360,496,"You're the Sinclair family's adopted daughter"],[500,663,"and Vice President Sinclair's fiancée."],[680,740,"Surely, they"],[740,893,"wouldn't be biased toward me, right?"],[986,1076,"Anne,"],[1140,1356,"even though you were fired from the company,"],[1360,1436,"you are still"],[1440,1593,"a member of the Sinclair family."],[1593,1743,"How could you do something like this?"],[1746,1913,"D*mn, it really is plagiarism."],[1913,2063,"-Yeah. -So shameless."],[2066,2196,"-So shameless. -Exactly."],[2210,2433,"Mr. Sinclair, as President of Sinclair Group,"],[2450,2603,"were you aware of this?"],[2843,2936,"Anne,"],[2963,3160,"this concerns the Sinclair Group's reputation."],[3186,3270,"Let's see if Arman"],[3270,3366,"will still help you."],[3410,3496,"Uncle Arman,"],[3560,3633,"Anne"],[3633,3750,"is plagiarizing"],[3753,3920,"our company's work."],[3953,4090,"This damages"],[4093,4296,"Sinclair Group's reputation and interests."],[4326,4540,"This is absolutely appalling."],[4600,4676,"Anne,"],[4753,4926,"do you have anything to say to everyone?"],[5226,5336,"It was Miss Blake"],[5340,5493,"who openly demanded I give my work"],[5493,5580,"to her."],[5583,5693,"When I refused,"],[5700,5853,"she took the chance while I wasn't looking"],[5853,6040,"and secretly stole my work."],[6043,6246,"Now she's even conspiring with others"],[6250,6363,"to slander me."],[6400,6486,"It's workplace bullying."],[6546,6650,"You're lying!"],[6733,6813,"Anne,"],[6850,6936,"this concerns"],[6940,7093,"the reputation of Sinclair Group."],[7110,7253,"Think carefully before you speak."],[7333,7456,"That idiot Anne,"],[7460,7616,"why has she changed?"],[7626,7763,"She actually betrayed me."],[7850,8033,"I'd like to ask Miss Blake,"],[8090,8203,"since you claim that Heartsea"],[8203,8320,"is your design,"],[8323,8500,"do you have the sketches"],[8503,8620,"from when you created it?"],[8733,8910,"I threw those away ages ago."],[8923,9106,"You threw yours away, but I have mine."]],"39":[[40,116,"Anne,"],[120,286,"this is a jewelry exhibition."],[290,416,"Can you stop making a scene?"],[416,526,"Vice President Sinclair,"],[530,700,"the Sinclair Group has a century-old legacy."],[723,886,"Both its credibility and reputation"],[890,1073,"are the best in the industry."],[1083,1176,"Moreover, Grandpa"],[1180,1323,"taught me from a young age"],[1356,1626,"to be honest and trustworthy,"],[1680,1903,"and to respect others' hard work."],[1930,2136,"Mr. Sinclair, are you giving me a hard time"],[2233,2413,"to shield a plagiarist?"],[2533,2690,"Yeah. Whoever produces the draft"],[2693,2858,"is the designer of this jewelry."],[2860,2993,"What is there to hide?"],[3203,3410,"These are my design sketches for Heartsea."],[3636,3793,"These really are the sketches for Heartsea."],[3793,3970,"Sketches can be faked."],[4040,4140,"You just drew them on the spot."],[4176,4380,"I knew you wouldn't admit it."],[4536,4646,"Let me borrow your computer."],[5252,5392,"-How could she do this? -It really was her."],[5394,5573,"-She really did it. -That's straight-up theft."],[5632,5766,"-Oh my god. -What a total disgrace."],[5768,5928,"-Grace didn't just copy it. -How could she do such a thing?"],[5940,6055,"-She stole it outright. -Yeah."],[6085,6213,"Get out of our industry!"],[6213,6323,"Miss Blake,"],[6360,6506,"you just said that"],[6506,6620,"plagiarists"],[6680,6903,"should go to jail, right?"]],"40":[[23,193,"You gave this design to me!"],[203,293,"I didn't steal it!"],[420,613,"So, Miss Blake, you're admitting2"],[650,880,"that Heartsea is indeed my work."],[890,1116,"You b*tch! You're lying!"],[1126,1276,"Whether I'm lying or not,"],[1290,1536,"the police will decide."],[2083,2180,"Which one of you is Grace?"],[2226,2320,"We received a report against her"],[2323,2440,"for stealing design drafts"],[2443,2606,"and spreading malicious rumors online"],[2606,2720,"to defame someone's character."],[2756,2863,"Officers,"],[2893,3063,"this is merely an internal company dispute."],[3066,3230,"We can resolve it privately."],[3230,3413,"We'll investigate if it's a misunderstanding."],[3463,3570,"You need to come with us."],[3800,3903,"Let go of me!"],[4006,4056,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[4056,4106,"Vice President Sinclair,"],[4110,4203,"your company's designers"],[4206,4343,"can't even plagiarize properly."],[4346,4406,"It's obvious at a glance"],[4410,4550,"who has the real talent."],[4570,4703,"So what?"],[4733,4866,"The designer of Heartsea,"],[4870,5106,"whether it's Grace or Anne,"],[5110,5176,"they are both"],[5180,5343,"designers for Sinclair Group."],[5373,5506,"Something you can only envy."],[5510,5656,"If I recall correctly,"],[5686,5833,"Vice President Sinclair fired Anne"],[5873,6006,"over a month ago."],[6246,6313,"Anne,"],[6313,6420,"I knew"],[6453,6586,"sending you home to focus on your work"],[6590,6663,"was the right decision."],[6666,6813,"Look, in just over a month,"],[6813,6983,"you've completed Heartsea to perfection."],[6986,7160,"You should come back to the office tomorrow."],[7220,7306,"Vice President Sinclair,"],[7353,7476,"I've been working at my new company"],[7480,7636,"for a month now."],[7690,7846,"The rights to Heartsea"],[7850,7966,"now belong to them as well."],[8040,8153,"Stop bluffing."],[8190,8346,"You've been blacklisted in the industry,"],[8366,8490,"so who would hire you?"],[8543,8646,"That's not something you need to worry about,"],[8650,8806,"Vice President Sinclair."],[8843,9073,"I haven't heard of any big brands hiring her."],[9126,9290,"She must be doing this to spite me."],[9470,9543,"Anne,"],[9580,9760,"I'm giving you a way out."],[9780,9913,"Don't be ungrateful."],[10006,10103,"Thank you,"],[10160,10256,"but I don't need"],[10310,10433,"your \"way out.\""]],"41":[[33,156,"With your educational background,"],[183,310,"aside from Sinclair Group,"],[326,503,"what major brand would hire you?"],[730,826,"Vice President Sinclair,"],[896,1063,"are you saying that the BC Group brand"],[1063,1180,"isn't big enough?"],[1286,1380,"Vice President Quinn?"],[1543,1710,"How do you know Vice President Quinn?"],[1720,1806,"Anne is the"],[1806,1943,"Design Director here at BC Group."],[1973,2100,"Is it strange that we know each other?"],[2123,2196,"What?"],[2366,2560,"You're BC Group's Design Director?"],[2753,2840,"How is that even possible?"],[2886,3013,"BC Group's designers"],[3013,3086,"are all graduates"],[3090,3223,"from top universities abroad."],[3273,3413,"Why would they hire Anne"],[3413,3526,"as their Design Director?"],[3593,3656,"Anne,"],[3700,3766,"congratulations."],[3800,3933,"Your debut collection secured the prime spot"],[3933,4090,"at the International Jewelry Exhibition."],[4160,4356,"We'll pop champagne back at the office."],[4360,4476,"Thank you, Vice President Quinn."],[4573,4650,"Anne,"],[4723,4890,"the Sinclair family raised you."],[4946,5033,"But BC Group is"],[5036,5200,"the Sinclair Group's rival."],[5236,5490,"This is a betrayal of the Sinclair Group."],[5533,5703,"Stop trying to guilt-trip me."],[5773,5943,"You were the one who betrayed me first."],[5986,6073,"I have never"],[6130,6286,"betrayed the Sinclair family."],[7340,7573,"Uncle Arman, did you see that?"],[7573,7676,"Anne has already"],[7680,7863,"escaped from the Sinclair family's control."],[7963,8053,"I saw it."],[8123,8256,"She's finally made something of herself."]],"42":[[263,330,"Vice President Sinclair,"],[330,473,"Miss Blake used her pregnancy"],[473,590,"to get released on bail."],[913,970,"Anne,"],[1036,1090,"Mr. Keane."],[1090,1260,"To celebrate our collection"],[1260,1413,"winning top spot at the Int'l Jewelry Expo,"],[1450,1583,"all the executives from the CEO’s Office"],[1583,1686,"will have dinner with you tonight."],[1703,1823,"All the executives?"],[1830,2003,"Will President Arman be there too?"],[2026,2090,"Uh"],[2170,2246,"he"],[2262,2409,"You want to have dinner with Arman?"],[2590,2780,"President Arman is very mysterious."],[2790,3052,"Even his own employees rarely see him."],[3070,3310,"I just really admire him, that's all."],[3343,3523,"So, would you be happy dining with him?"],[3543,3776,"Of course. He's my idol."],[3776,3886,"He's your idol?"],[4023,4136,"Back when I was at my lowest"],[4136,4378,"after being betrayed,"],[4440,4566,"it was watching President Arman"],[4570,4723,"sharing his Hill University"],[4730,4940,"study notes and campus life updates"],[4990,5183,"that helped me focus on my studies"],[5266,5400,"and kept my mind from wandering."],[5412,5504,"Wow."],[5603,5746,"That's so romantic."],[5750,5830,"Miss Sinclair,"],[5880,6026,"you and President Arman"],[6026,6156,"you aren't in an online relationship, right?"],[6250,6330,"No."],[6333,6563,"I just simply admire him."],[6580,6750,"Then let Arman join the dinner tonight."],[6800,7113,"Boss, aren't you trying to stay mysterious?"],[7203,7280,"Uncle Arman?"],[7344,7543,"Have you forgotten your identity?"],[7560,7743,"You're the CEO of the Sinclair Group now."],[7763,7893,"How can you order Mr. Quinn around?"],[7896,7942,"Yes."],[7976,8106,"I'll arrange it immediately."],[8223,8373,"Why does Vice President Quinn"],[8373,8503,"listen to everything Arman says?"],[8596,8716,"And is Arman someone"],[8720,8926,"Vice President Quinn can just order around?"]],"43":[[780,870,"Uncle Arman."],[1006,1146,"Uncle Arman, what are you doing here?"],[1146,1326,"This is BC Group's celebration."],[1353,1486,"You're the President of Sinclair Group."],[1491,1614,"It's not appropriate for you to be here."],[1666,1783,"It's fine."],[1823,1993,"As the President of Sinclair Group,"],[1993,2160,"I'm here to meet your BC President"],[2170,2270,"and see how we compare."],[2486,2573,"Let me tell you,"],[2603,2713,"that President Arman"],[2716,2813,"is incredibly mysterious."],[2820,2906,"Did you check with"],[2953,3080,"Vice President Quinn and Arman"],[3086,3180,"before showing up?"],[3483,3770,"You've only been at BC Group for a few days,"],[3770,3960,"and you're already siding with your boss?"],[3960,4150,"I'm not siding with him."],[4153,4236,"It's just"],[4263,4430,"respect. Pure respect."],[4780,4863,"If they decide"],[4863,5000,"to kick me out later,"],[5000,5126,"will you back me up?"],[5326,5443,"You should just leave now,"],[5443,5660,"before they get here."],[5660,5790,"Hey, hurry up."],[5790,5933,"You're sitting in the host's seat!"],[5993,6140,"Come on, let's go."],[6623,6786,"BC Group's Global Marketing Director,"],[6786,6946,"Angel, is here too?"],[6986,7070,"Vice President Quinn,"],[7149,7306,"my uncle just wanted to meet"],[7308,7420,"President Arman."],[7519,7620,"President Arman."],[7666,7763,"President Arman."],[8263,8333,"What's the matter?"],[8423,8573,"Overjoyed to see your idol?"],[8580,8653,"You're"],[8726,8876,"President Arman?"]],"44":[[36,113,"Anne,"],[146,400,"Mr. Sinclair is BC Group's Global President,"],[416,490,"Arman."],[803,950,"I can't believe Arman is actually"],[953,1060,"the one who spent five years"],[1060,1223,"building a top jewelry brand,"],[1223,1420,"the founder of BC Group, Arman."],[1456,1600,"Is this a surprise,"],[1620,1733,"or a shock?"],[1830,1913,"A surprise."],[2073,2180,"Why are you zoning out?"],[2230,2353,"Sit down and take a break."],[2663,2780,"The Arman who comforted me,"],[2783,2883,"encouraged me,"],[2963,3170,"and got me through my lows,"],[3220,3366,"is actually Arman."],[3463,3640,"You'd better work hard at BC Group."],[3673,3806,"I won't pull any strings for you"],[3810,3916,"just because of our relationship."],[3943,4070,"I think Director Sinclair's talent"],[4073,4170,"doesn't need any strings pulled."],[4173,4310,"Her Heartsea collection in Hartford,"],[4313,4430,"just two hours into the presale,"],[4433,4590,"has already made over ten million dollars."],[4593,4632,"Really?"],[4633,4686,"Anne,"],[4770,4846,"congratulations."],[4883,4996,"Your debut collection"],[5000,5136,"has achieved such great results."],[5150,5283,"Welcome to BC Group."],[5303,5433,"Thank you, Vice President Quinn."],[5436,5560,"Thank you, Director Angel."],[6103,6190,"Easy on the wine."],[6220,6310,"Don't drink too much."],[6316,6473,"I'm fine, I can drink."],[6476,6533,"Mr. Quinn,"],[7223,7370,"is there anyone else you want to toast?"],[7636,7720,"Uncle Arman,"],[7783,7870,"here's to you,"],[8290,8413,"President Arman."],[8780,8926,"I've been completely humiliated."],[8943,9138,"Why does Anne get to join BC Group,"],[9150,9293,"and even become the Design Director?"],[9970,10083,"Anne?"],[10410,10557,"Take care of your health, Arman."],[10663,10740,"Arman,"],[10793,10906,"the boss of BC Group."]],"45":[[133,270,"I knew Anne got into BC Group"],[273,436,"through underhanded means."],[466,550,"Are you okay?"],[930,1056,"Uncle Arman,"],[1450,1536,"Arman,"],[1766,2010,"the President of BC Group."],[2030,2316,"You don't need Sinclair Group at all,"],[2480,2756,"so why do you insist on marrying me?"],[2890,3050,"Because I like you,"],[3100,3196,"silly."],[3250,3376,"Like me?"],[3480,3556,"Yes."],[3693,3793,"I like you."],[5506,5600,"Anne,"],[5626,5819,"your wedding to Gavin is in a few days."],[5833,5980,"You humiliated me in public,"],[6003,6170,"so I'll ruin your reputation too,"],[6180,6316,"and get you kicked out of the Sinclair family."],[7170,7280,"I won't give you up"],[7283,7433,"to anyone ever again."]],"46":[[6,70,"I don't care about"],[73,180,"your business dealings."],[190,293,"The wedding will proceed as planned."],[306,436,"You'd better clean up"],[440,526,"that mess you made outside."],[526,603,"If you do anything"],[603,686,"to hurt Anne again,"],[690,820,"get the hell out of the Sinclair family."],[860,986,"Understood, Grandpa."],[1006,1083,"Anne,"],[1120,1193,"if you're ever mistreated,"],[1193,1306,"tell me immediately."],[1343,1480,"I won't let him off easy."],[2090,2180,"Anne,"],[2183,2326,"Grace was really shaken up,"],[2360,2466,"and it's affected the baby."],[2500,2666,"She needs to rest and recover now."],[2750,2900,"So go tell Grandpa"],[2933,3086,"to keep the wedding low-key."],[3590,3696,"Gavin,"],[3803,3966,"then let's just call off the wedding."],[4630,4703,"Uncle Arman,"],[4780,4926,"will you be coming to"],[4986,5073,"my wedding to Gavin?"],[5733,5880,"Aren't you afraid I'll steal the bride?"],[6033,6110,"Be my guest."]],"47":[[1706,1766,"I can't."],[1766,1920,"The makeup artist is waiting for me."],[2573,2620,"Hello?"],[2676,2810,"I've got a huge scoop for you."],[2846,2993,"The Sinclair Group's new bride"],[2996,3236,"is cheating with an old man at the wedding."],[3236,3326,"Wait, what?"],[3326,3433,"We're on our way."],[3700,3800,"Anne,"],[3833,4020,"you're dead this time."],[4116,4236,"We were doing the bride's makeup,"],[4236,4323,"but halfway through,"],[4326,4446,"she took a call"],[4453,4540,"and rushed out."],[4626,4770,"Did you bully Anne again"],[4770,4886,"and make her angry?"],[4923,5043,"No, I didn't."],[5123,5206,"Gavin."],[5208,5290,"Chairman."],[5296,5416,"You said you didn't,"],[5427,5533,"but this trashy woman"],[5563,5726,"is making a scene at the wedding."],[5806,5921,"What are you doing here?"],[5929,6016,"Chairman,"],[6016,6198,"I'm not the trashy one."],[6206,6323,"Anne is."],[6330,6483,"Gavin, let me tell you,"],[6493,6556,"Anne"],[6563,6664,"is cheating on you."],[6740,6846,"What are you talking about?"],[6853,6970,"I'm not making this up."],[6976,7086,"Anne is having an affair."],[7090,7180,"An affair?"],[7210,7303,"If word gets out,"],[7306,7406,"the damage to the Sinclair family's reputation"],[7410,7503,"will be immense."],[7506,7696,"I watched Anne grow up."],[7716,7833,"I know what kind of person she is."],[7836,7970,"So stop spewing nonsense here"],[7971,8070,"and slandering Anne."],[8076,8156,"Chairman,"],[8162,8320,"you have to believe me."],[8323,8413,"I saw it with my own eyes."],[8413,8540,"She and the president of BC Group"],[8543,8693,"were having sex in the car."]],"48":[[30,227,"Did you see the BC Group President,"],[228,323,"Arman?"],[410,473,"Yes."],[560,726,"He's a very old man."],[740,896,"\"Take care of your health, Arman.\""],[953,1050,"Angel told Harlan"],[1053,1166,"to remind the elderly President"],[1166,1260,"to watch his health."],[1313,1423,"He must be an old man."],[1506,1590,"Brother,"],[1603,1731,"the Sinclair family will never allow"],[1733,1896,"such a promiscuous woman into our home."],[1900,2003,"That's right, Brother."],[2016,2146,"Anne isn't that kind of person."],[2166,2276,"They are so brazen that"],[2280,2432,"they're meeting in secret upstairs right now."],[2446,2649,"If you don't believe me, we can catch them."],[2653,2823,"She's got some nerve."],[2826,2916,"She clearly has no respect for Gavin"],[2920,3063,"or the Sinclair family."],[3066,3170,"Take me there."],[3203,3306,"Make way, make way."],[3393,3466,"Chairman,"],[3470,3563,"did you know your grandson's wife"],[3563,3683,"and the BC Group President"],[3686,3763,"are having an affair?"],[3766,3836,"Shut up."],[3870,3976,"Who invited you?"],[4003,4106,"Anne and the BC Group President"],[4110,4210,"are right inside this room."],[4210,4353,"I saw them go in with my own eyes."],[4373,4480,"The BC Group President?"],[4483,4590,"None of us have ever seen him."],[4653,4796,"I've seen the BC Group President."],[4800,4936,"He's a very old man."],[4940,5063,"He surely has a family already."],[5063,5186,"Mrs. Sinclair"],[5190,5362,"is a cheater and a homewrecker."],[5373,5440,"Vice President Sinclair,"],[5440,5550,"how does it feel to get cuckolded?"],[5553,5650,"Any comments?"],[5683,5796,"F*ck your comments!"],[5820,5943,"Who let you in?"],[6006,6080,"Open the door."],[6083,6150,"Vice President Sinclair,"],[6160,6303,"the room you want us to open"],[6306,6430,"was booked by the president of BC Group."],[6430,6616,"We don't have the authority to open it."],[6633,6746,"Did you hear that?"],[6766,6860,"Open it."],[6863,6976,"Well"],[6976,7050,"I really"],[7100,7186,"Anne,"],[7190,7303,"you sl*t!"],[7306,7416,"Open the door!"],[7840,7878,"Hey!"],[8050,8120,"Gavin."],[8160,8226,"Grandpa."],[8260,8356,"You all"],[8360,8446,"Anne,"],[8473,8603,"tell your lover to come out!"],[8673,8796,"What lover?"]],"49":[[13,116,"Anne,"],[120,286,"you've got some nerve acting this calm."],[293,453,"We caught you red-handed, so stop pretending."],[453,613,"You're sleeping with the CEO of BC Group."],[616,726,"I saw it with my own eyes."],[800,866,"Grandpa,"],[870,1083,"I only went to BC Group for work."],[1100,1143,"I really didn't do"],[1143,1250,"anything to betray"],[1253,1363,"the Sinclair family."],[1363,1503,"The waiter said"],[1530,1723,"this is the BC Group President's room."],[1730,1860,"Grace saw you two"],[1860,2003,"doing dirty things."],[2003,2130,"How cheap can you be,"],[2143,2340,"hooking up with an old man for money?"],[2343,2416,"Gavin,"],[2460,2550,"I really didn't do"],[2553,2680,"anything to betray you."],[2680,2830,"Just tell the reporters to leave."],[2833,2940,"Anne,"],[2943,3066,"if you didn't betray Gavin,"],[3070,3146,"what are you afraid of?"],[3163,3270,"Exactly."],[3310,3403,"She definitely did something"],[3403,3520,"shameful."],[3540,3633,"Where's the lover?"],[3636,3773,"Drag that lover out here!"],[3823,4013,"Gavin, don't be rash."],[4076,4193,"If you keep blocking me,"],[4196,4350,"I won't hold back."],[4580,4673,"Arman."],[4690,4860,"Come out, you old b*stard!"],[5103,5310,"Isn't this BC Group's Vice President Quinn"],[5360,5540,"and Marketing Director Angel?"],[5556,5616,"Grandpa,"],[5620,5860,"I had a small project"],[5860,6023,"with some tricky issues."],[6056,6163,"Vice President Quinn knew that I"],[6163,6270,"was getting married today,"],[6290,6403,"That's why she came to the hotel to see me,"],[6403,6526,"for an impromptu meeting,"],[6543,6673,"which ran a little long."],[6700,6803,"That's not true!"],[6833,6920,"I heard with my own ears"],[6920,7063,"Vice President Quinn tell Anne that"],[7063,7236,"the BC Group President was waiting for her."],[7240,7336,"Anne,"],[7340,7446,"where is President Arman?"],[7586,7720,"I am President Arman."],[7816,7930,"Is there a problem?"]],"50":[[96,306,"Arman, what are you doing here?"],[480,593,"Uncle Arman."],[633,770,"Who did you just say you were?"],[840,963,"I apologize, President Arman."],[983,1176,"I don't know how these people barged in."],[1240,1386,"You called him President Arman?"],[1386,1473,"That's right."],[1526,1720,"This is the President of BC Group,"],[1723,1780,"Arman."],[1803,1933,"With Vice President Quinn confirming it,"],[1933,2010,"it must be true."],[2026,2190,"I didn't expect BC Group's President Arman"],[2193,2310,"to actually be Arman."],[2314,2470,"The mysterious founder of BC Group,"],[2470,2526,"Arman,"],[2530,2753,"is actually Mr. Sinclair."],[2800,2966,"Then BC Group belongs to the Sinclairs too."],[2973,3056,"This is shocking."],[3084,3190,"Yes, Mr. Sinclair."],[3193,3290,"In five years, Mr. Sinclair"],[3293,3506,"built a world-class jewelry brand."],[3516,3650,"Like father, like son."],[3663,3800,"Hahaha."],[3820,4093,"My son has always worked hard."],[4320,4396,"No."],[4403,4513,"That's impossible."],[4570,4793,"How can Arman be BC Group's President?"],[4900,5006,"Didn't you say BC Group's President"],[5010,5133,"was an old man?"],[5140,5316,"I... I heard it."],[5333,5456,"Where were you,"],[5460,5573,"and when did you hear that?"],[5583,5706,"Just two weeks ago,"],[5710,5863,"on the night of the jewelry competition."],[5866,5943,"I saw it with my own eyes,"],[5943,6070,"and heard it with my own ears."],[6086,6240,"Vice President Quinn told Angel"],[6246,6406,"that Anne and Old Man Arman"],[6430,6550,"were hooking up in the car."],[6588,6672,"Hooking up!"],[6733,6906,"How is that even possible?"],[6933,7183,"Isn't that Anne"],[7186,7366,"with Mr. Sinclair?"],[7376,7668,"Could Mr. Sinclair and his niece-in-law"],[7773,7903,"That is absolutely impossible."],[7910,8073,"I watched Anne grow up."],[8073,8276,"She has always been obedient and sensible."],[8310,8576,"And Arman is a man of integrity."],[8593,8726,"There's no way"],[8730,8913,"he's having an affair with his niece-in-law."],[8913,9050,"I couldn't have heard it wrong."],[9090,9226,"If there's nothing going on between them,"],[9230,9386,"why would he help her get into BC Group?"],[9423,9503,"Grandpa,"],[9503,9720,"I was being cyberbullied a while back,"],[9733,9936,"and Uncle Arman feared I'd harm myself,"],[9946,10103,"so he hired me at BC Group."],[10113,10150,"I see."],[10173,10286,"Your Uncle Arman takes after me in that."],[10286,10410,"He knows to look after the family"],[10413,10533,"and care for the younger generation."],[10543,10650,"That's not true!"],[10650,10733,"I saw Anne"],[10733,10860,"and Arman in a car,"],[10870,11006,"and it was rocking back and forth!"],[11036,11103,"Sister,"],[11153,11260,"get this filthy trash"],[11262,11426,"out of here! Throw her out!"],[11433,11510,"Get out! Move it!"],[11513,11686,"Let go of me! Let go!"],[11746,11813,"Gavin!"],[11813,11960,"I'm pregnant with your child!"],[11963,12040,"A child?"],[12123,12213,"There's a child involved?"],[12213,12323,"She's actually pregnant?"],[12350,12413,"Grandpa,"],[12470,12563,"since Miss Blake"],[12563,12700,"is already here,"],[12720,12856,"and Gavin doesn't trust me,"],[12880,12996,"maybe we should cancel the wedding."],[13036,13123,"Just let it go."]],"51":[[216,303,"No, absolutely not."],[316,510,"Grandpa, we can't cancel it."],[693,866,"Anne, I'm begging you."],[876,953,"It's all my fault."],[966,1096,"Stop this, okay?"],[1100,1153,"Gavin,"],[1223,1370,"if we don't cancel the wedding,"],[1400,1563,"what about Miss Blake's child?"],[1590,1763,"Do you expect me to raise it?"],[1786,2000,"She's already pregnant out of wedlock."],[2013,2143,"What happens when the baby is born?"],[2283,2396,"Grandpa,"],[2396,2603,"I just want to focus on work right now,"],[2710,2830,"help Uncle Arman"],[2833,3013,"make BC Group the best in the world."],[3073,3146,"Anne,"],[3220,3296,"my dear child,"],[3326,3430,"regarding today's events,"],[3433,3606,"I misunderstood you."],[3613,3683,"Don't worry,"],[3686,3800,"when it comes to marriage,"],[3806,3950,"I won't force you."],[4070,4216,"Thank you, Grandpa."],[4406,4500,"Gavin,"],[4500,4583,"Anne and your Uncle Arman"],[4586,4673,"are definitely having an affair."],[4673,4813,"You have to believe me."],[4816,4900,"Where's the proof?"],[4923,5110,"Grandpa has always favored Arman."],[5113,5392,"Now that he's revealed as BC Group's President,"],[5406,5492,"and I've lost"],[5493,5633,"my lucky charm, Anne,"],[5673,5806,"how am I supposed to fight him?"],[5810,5996,"Gavin, I didn't know either"],[5996,6140,"that Arman was actually your uncle."],[6143,6280,"If you hadn't made a scene,"],[6293,6482,"I would have married Anne by now"],[6483,6656,"and inherited the Sinclair Group."],[6656,6813,"It's all your fault, you idiot."],[6843,6934,"Get out!"],[6934,7007,"Ah!"],[7190,7240,"Ah!"],[7566,7643,"Grace!"]],"52":[[3,170,"The ancestors have blessed us."],[196,486,"Arman has finally made something of himself."],[670,763,"Arman,"],[796,1026,"come here and pay your respects."],[1090,1166,"Alright."],[2070,2133,"By the way,"],[2153,2320,"your eldest aunt told me today"],[2320,2586,"that her niece, Diana,"],[2590,2736,"whom you've known since childhood,"],[2736,2866,"is about your age."],[2870,3006,"Why don't you meet her?"],[3226,3303,"No need."],[3420,3506,"I already have a girlfriend."],[3510,3633,"You have a girlfriend?"],[3680,3810,"Which family is she from?"],[4050,4256,"Why are you always so evasive?"],[4363,4436,"Anne."],[4473,4676,"Have you met Uncle Arman's girlfriend?"],[4856,4963,"No, I haven't."],[4973,5163,"Anne works directly under you,"],[5173,5303,"and even she says she hasn't seen her."],[5323,5396,"Let me ask you,"],[5400,5516,"are you still being some"],[5520,5656,"shameful, secretive"],[5660,5766,"male homewrecker?"],[5780,5856,"No."],[5973,6066,"I'm about to become official."],[6170,6406,"That kills any hope I had left."],[6470,6653,"In front of our ancestors,"],[6720,6863,"you still show no remorse."],[6900,6980,"Grandpa,"],[7023,7150,"we came here today"],[7153,7300,"to share good news with the ancestors."],[7313,7466,"Don't get upset with Uncle Arman"],[7466,7603,"over such a small thing."],[7673,7820,"Anne is right."],[8136,8226,"Ancestors,"],[8230,8506,"bless the Sinclair family with peace,"],[8516,8683,"and prosperity for our descendants."]],"53":[[240,476,"Anne, stay a moment."],[480,650,"Grandpa has a few words for you."],[670,746,"Okay."],[770,940,"I asked Anne to stay,"],[940,1076,"not you."],[1080,1160,"You can go."],[1260,1346,"Oh."],[2083,2173,"Anne,"],[2256,2393,"how does Grandpa treat you?"],[2460,2616,"You treat me very well,"],[2620,2823,"like your own granddaughter."],[2860,2953,"Then if Grandpa"],[2953,3076,"asks you something,"],[3096,3240,"you mustn't hide anything."],[3310,3403,"Please, ask."],[3416,3490,"Have you noticed"],[3493,3636,"Uncle Arman at the office,"],[3636,3836,"which married female colleague"],[3840,3966,"he is close to?"],[4050,4143,"No."],[4143,4320,"Uncle Arman rarely comes to the office."],[4320,4503,"I hardly ever see him there."],[4543,4650,"Then could you"],[4693,4800,"get me a list"],[4800,4933,"of all the married female colleagues"],[4933,5033,"in the company?"],[5050,5303,"Grandpa, did you keep me here"],[5333,5550,"just to ask me to do this?"],[5580,5653,"Look,"],[5676,5826,"your Uncle Arman,"],[5830,6013,"he's lost his head over a woman."],[6046,6126,"He's very protective of her."],[6150,6290,"So regarding this matter,"],[6290,6423,"you absolutely cannot let him know."],[6430,6540,"It has to be just between us,"],[6540,6653,"working in secret."],[6793,6866,"Okay."],[6873,6960,"So,"],[6960,7066,"you need to find out which"],[7070,7233,"female colleague he's close to."],[7236,7390,"Let me know right away."],[7473,7566,"Okay."]],"54":[[320,413,"Uncle Arman,"],[686,780,"Uncle Arman,"],[836,1006,"hurry back to your room."],[1010,1190,"When Grandpa kept you back today,"],[1200,1300,"what did he say?"],[1390,1650,"He asked me to help him investigate"],[1686,1863,"who you're being a homewrecker for."],[1976,2060,"Did you agree?"],[2126,2310,"Grandpa treats me so well."],[2316,2423,"Us being like this."],[2510,2556,"Sigh,"],[4213,4366,"since Grandpa treats you so well,"],[4516,4626,"shouldn't you give him a few"],[4626,4773,"chubby great-grandsons?"],[5003,5280,"Because I like you, silly."],[5410,5590,"Why would the wonderful Arman"],[5710,5866,"like me?"]],"55":[[40,163,"Ever since Vice President Sinclair"],[163,333,"took over the Sinclair Group,"],[336,503,"because of Miss Blake's plagiarism"],[503,676,"and Vice President Sinclair's scandals,"],[736,833,"our stock prices have plunged."],[850,960,"At this rate,"],[980,1123,"the company will collapse sooner or later."],[1140,1203,"That's because"],[1203,1330,"the people your Design Department hired"],[1333,1456,"are just a bunch of useless losers."],[1473,1666,"What kind of garbage are they designing?"],[1673,1810,"If Vice President Sinclair hadn't let"],[1813,1956,"Grace steal Anne's work,"],[1956,2140,"Heartsea would belong to the Sinclair Group."],[2143,2266,"That's three hundred million in sales."],[2270,2476,"Miss Sinclair recently released"],[2480,2593,"two more hit designs."],[2603,2760,"The presales alone are going crazy."],[2763,2936,"Chairman, since BC Group"],[2940,3043,"also belongs to Mr. Sinclair,"],[3043,3203,"we suggest asking Mr. Sinclair"],[3206,3346,"to co-manage the Sinclair Group."],[3373,3523,"That way, Miss Sinclair can come back"],[3523,3660,"and design products for us too."],[3710,3786,"I agree."],[3870,3980,"Who do you think you are?"],[3980,4073,"How many shares do you own"],[4073,4196,"that you dare make suggestions here?"],[4200,4276,"Enough."],[4343,4470,"And who do you think you are?"],[4516,4703,"You make mistakes and refuse to repent,"],[4710,4810,"yet you have the nerve to stand here"],[4810,4946,"and act all high and mighty."],[4960,5126,"Go home and reflect on your actions."],[5376,5440,"Grandpa,"],[5520,5633,"I know I was wrong."],[5653,5693,"I handed Anne to you"],[5693,5926,"like a sharp blade,"],[5933,6080,"but you didn't cherish her."],[6103,6290,"What's the use of admitting it now?"],[6360,6433,"Alright."],[6493,6646,"I'll discuss your proposal"],[6646,6810,"with Arman."]],"56":[[56,140,"Thank you."],[204,324,"Anne,"],[330,503,"how's the matter I asked you to handle?"],[503,650,"I've looked into it, Grandpa."],[653,796,"Our company doesn't have any"],[796,923,"young married employees."],[923,1060,"They're either single,"],[1073,1266,"or in their forties or fifties."],[1276,1426,"Could it be that because"],[1430,1626,"Uncle Arman's mother died young,"],[1630,1823,"he has mommy issues?"],[1876,1963,"No, no, no."],[1976,2060,"Absolutely not."],[2060,2123,"Grandpa,"],[2123,2360,"right now, the directors at Sinclair Group"],[2363,2536,"are all united against Gavin,"],[2556,2770,"and want Arman to take over the company."],[2773,2910,"But all I want is"],[2913,3070,"for him to settle down soon"],[3073,3220,"and give me a chubby grandson."],[3483,3590,"With everything going on,"],[3596,3793,"he's still out partying!"],[4080,4163,"Sigh."],[4183,4280,"Anne,"],[4313,4440,"regarding Uncle Arman,"],[4443,4596,"please talk some sense into him for me."],[4636,4733,"Okay, I will."]],"57":[[650,730,"Gavin?"],[960,1100,"Why aren't you asleep?"],[1100,1220,"What are you doing in my room?"],[1310,1523,"What did Grandpa want you to tell Arman?"],[1610,1850,"To convince him to manage the Sinclair Group?"],[2046,2116,"No."],[2126,2263,"Then what was it?"],[2346,2456,"Anne,"],[2470,2603,"I'm being targeted by the entire"],[2603,2766,"senior management of the Sinclair Group."],[2766,2970,"Grandpa sent me home to reflect."],[2986,3130,"Are you satisfied now?"],[3140,3323,"You brought that on yourself."],[3366,3506,"What has it got to do with me?"],[3543,3733,"You ask what it has to do with you?"],[3810,3980,"Grace lost the baby."],[3983,4153,"I'm done with her."],[4153,4333,"So stop making a scene, okay?"],[4386,4546,"Grace lost the baby?"],[4756,4856,"Gavin,"],[4876,5083,"I never intended to fight with you."],[5193,5233,"Enough."],[5243,5410,"I don't want to talk about this right now."],[5443,5590,"It's late. Go back to your room."],[5613,5843,"You're just jealous of Grace, aren't you?"],[5866,6030,"I'll give you what you want right now."],[6086,6143,"What are you doing?"],[6146,6203,"Let go!"],[6206,6396,"What are you doing? Let me go!"],[6410,6466,"Isn't this exactly"],[6473,6600,"what you wanted me to do to you?"],[6623,6780,"Stop pretending!"],[6780,6876,"Anne,"],[6886,7066,"without me, you'd be dead by now."],[7078,7206,"You ingrate!"],[7213,7400,"How dare you betray me."],[7826,7983,"Uncle Arman, help me!"]],"58":[[1010,1100,"Uncle Arman,"],[1106,1283,"Anne is my fiancée."],[1290,1460,"What gives you the right to barge in?"],[1466,1546,"Wait for me."],[2304,2401,"Gavin,"],[2430,2616,"if you dare touch her again,"],[2643,2793,"I'll kill you."],[2826,2946,"Arman,"],[2980,3163,"don't forget who you are."],[3206,3400,"She's your niece-in-law!"],[3443,3643,"If I can get you fired,"],[3693,3886,"I can kick you out of the Sinclair family."],[3946,4083,"Try me."],[5863,6073,"My only chance to make a comeback now,"],[6080,6230,"is to marry Anne."],[6293,6453,"I can't give up."]],"59":[[246,333,"Here, drink some water."],[393,470,"It'll help calm your nerves."],[630,700,"Thanks."],[746,896,"I'm fine now."],[913,1066,"Don't worry about me."],[1373,1576,"I'll head back now."],[2240,2316,"Anne."],[2460,2553,"Marry me."],[2693,2870,"But... But I"],[2873,3076,"When you called for me to save you,"],[3190,3446,"it proves you like me too, right?"],[3510,3903,"Do... Do I like him too?"],[4006,4163,"Uncle Arman, save me!"],[4280,4453,"At that moment,"],[4490,4613,"the very first person"],[4616,4733,"I thought of was actually him"],[4960,5076,"Arman."],[5150,5383,"Give me some time to think."],[5466,5613,"I'm going on a business trip for a few days."],[5640,5763,"When I get back,"],[5763,5996,"give me your answer, okay?"]],"60":[[418,505,"President."],[516,630,"The clothes they bought this time"],[633,720,"are all really nice."],[723,810,"Where did they come from?"],[850,1026,"Gavin sent them over."],[1058,1223,"He bought several outfits for every child."],[1246,1350,"He brought them here?"],[1353,1426,"Yeah."],[1433,1543,"When was this?"],[1566,1730,"Why didn't you mention it to me?"],[1730,1860,"He's been here quite a few times."],[1860,2020,"He said you asked him to bring them."],[2053,2113,"Hey,"],[2113,2183,"look at that drawing."],[2183,2350,"Gavin drew that himself too."],[2883,3010,"This is you, Sister."],[3010,3160,"And this is Uncle."],[3580,3746,"Who told you to draw here?"],[3746,3833,"You can't draw here."],[3833,3943,"Hurry, go."],[4083,4210,"It's fine, let her draw."],[4260,4460,"Don't scold her for drawing anymore."],[5210,5303,"Thank you."],[5430,5540,"Silly."],[5843,5933,"What do I do?"],[6020,6110,"I think I really"],[6113,6270,"have fallen for that demon."],[7866,7946,"Cheers."],[8230,8420,"Will the spring breeze carry my thoughts"],[8430,8580,"to you while you're away?"],[8590,8676,"Everyone, keep eating."],[9353,9516,"Mr. Sinclair, you're suddenly so happy."],[9563,9700,"Is there some good news?"],[9840,9923,"We secured the project"],[9930,10070,"we've been preparing for twelve years."]],"61":[[153,303,"I'm far away on business,"],[306,440,"but receiving your message,"],[453,630,"my heart has flown back to Seaside City."],[690,806,"Anne,"],[883,996,"did you see your Uncle Arman's"],[996,1140,"post on social media?"],[1286,1433,"What post?"],[1440,1503,"Oh my,"],[1503,1566,"take a look."],[1596,1783,"He's getting bolder and bolder,"],[1786,2016,"confessing his love publicly like that."],[2023,2120,"How does he not even realize"],[2120,2353,"he's acting like a homewrecker?"],[2410,2556,"Why didn't that rascal even set"],[2560,2726,"his privacy settings?"],[2880,3030,"Grandpa, don't worry."],[3040,3223,"Uncle Arman is an adult."],[3246,3480,"He knows what he's doing."],[3486,3616,"If he knew what he was doing,"],[3633,3796,"he wouldn't be a homewrecker."],[3893,3983,"Grandpa,"],[3986,4133,"let me ask you something."],[4163,4476,"If the woman Uncle Arman likes"],[4480,4633,"is actually single now,"],[4700,4863,"would you approve of them being together?"],[4910,5053,"I absolutely cannot accept that."],[5053,5220,"I won't let the Sinclair family"],[5223,5420,"be the target of public scorn."],[5463,5573,"If Grandpa knew"],[5573,5743,"that the person Uncle Arman likes is me,"],[5810,6000,"he'd find it even harder to accept."],[6006,6076,"Anne,"],[6160,6216,"did your Uncle Arman"],[6220,6396,"bribe you?"],[6403,6500,"No, not at all."],[6713,6816,"Lately,"],[6860,7030,"I've been so worried I can't sleep."],[7030,7113,"He still"],[7113,7206,"hasn't gotten married,"],[7223,7376,"making me ashamed to show my face."],[7380,7593,"or Old Man Su will laugh at me."],[7640,7756,"Grandpa, don't"],[8170,8336,"What... what's wrong?"],[8553,8633,"I'm fine."],[8636,8770,"Maybe I ate too many dumplings"],[8860,8963,"at the orphanage tonight."],[8990,9113,"Ask Lana to get you some"],[9213,9300,"stomach medicine."],[9303,9433,"Get some rest."],[9433,9530,"Alright."],[11100,11236,"What's wrong with me?"],[11390,11573,"My period is late."],[11726,11810,"Don't tell me"],[11946,12100,"I'm pregnant?"]],"62":[[56,166,"You're five weeks pregnant."],[170,293,"Make sure to get plenty of rest"],[293,416,"and eat nutritious food."],[483,560,"I"],[606,713,"I"],[767,1027,"I'm pregnant with Arman's baby."],[1896,2003,"Doctor,"],[2003,2116,"I'm the fiancé of Anne,"],[2120,2260,"who was just here."],[2263,2356,"The two of us"],[2360,2523,"have been arguing recently,"],[2543,2656,"so she wouldn't let me come in with her."],[2696,2786,"I wanted to ask,"],[2790,2923,"how is she doing?"],[2943,3050,"She's pregnant."],[3063,3236,"Mood swings are normal."],[3240,3403,"As her husband, you need to be patient."],[3510,3606,"Pregnant"],[3783,3860,"Anne,"],[3896,4086,"no matter whose baby you're carrying,"],[4116,4263,"to inherit the Sinclair Group,"],[4303,4460,"you can only be mine."],[6283,6400,"Hello, Uncle Arman."],[6473,6586,"When are you coming back?"],[6740,6830,"Miss me?"],[7103,7216,"I have something important"],[7220,7320,"to tell you."],[7423,7566,"What's the big news?"],[7656,7846,"You'll find out when you get back."],[7872,7922,"Okay."],[7928,8113,"Let me know when you're back."],[8260,8370,"Anne, look out!"],[8926,9053,"Gavin, are you okay?"],[9063,9136,"Anne,"],[9190,9286,"watch where you're going."],[9630,9773,"Why are you breathing so heavily?"],[9783,9870,"Let's go to the hospital."]],"63":[[23,290,"You'll get the money as soon as it's done."],[1513,1616,"Doc... Doctor,"],[1650,1773,"how is he doing?"],[1773,1846,"Does the patient have a history"],[1850,1976,"of severe asthma?"],[1986,2110,"And did he exert himself"],[2113,2233,"during an attack?"],[3733,3820,"Are you okay?"],[3850,3973,"Do you need a checkup?"],[4140,4316,"I think so."],[4320,4490,"The patient has respiratory failure."],[4540,4706,"Respiratory failure"],[4806,4880,"You should try your best"],[4920,5063,"to fulfill his wishes."],[6573,6650,"Anne."],[6720,6876,"Am I going to die?"],[7353,7446,"Gavin,"],[7450,7583,"just focus on getting better."],[7593,7723,"Don't lie to me."],[7833,7930,"I know my own body"],[7933,8050,"better than anyone."],[8100,8193,"I'm not going to make it."],[8210,8443,"This is all your fault."],[8446,8633,"Stop pretending to care."],[8673,8750,"I'm sorry."],[8783,8940,"I don't want your apologies."],[8943,9086,"I want you to marry me."]],"64":[[110,213,"I can't do that."],[486,563,"Why?"],[593,790,"Are you in love with Uncle Arman?"],[1126,1256,"I ended up with a terminal illness"],[1260,1363,"trying to save you,"],[1363,1470,"yet while you were still"],[1473,1630,"engaged to me,"],[1630,1806,"you were sleeping with Uncle Arman."],[1853,2046,"If word of this gets out,"],[2093,2260,"think about the impact on Arman,"],[2263,2370,"on BC Group,"],[2373,2600,"and on the Sinclair family!"],[3253,3306,"Anne,"],[3346,3490,"I don't have much time left."],[3510,3616,"Come back to me."],[3660,3773,"Help me fulfill my dream"],[3773,3860,"of taking the highest position"],[3863,4013,"at Sinclair Group."],[4103,4180,"Will you?"],[4866,5060,"Baby, I've just landed."],[5206,5376,"The always mysterious President of BC Group,"],[5380,5440,"Arman,"],[5443,5576,"has made his first public appearance."],[5580,5750,"The wedding of the Third Prince of Hola"],[5763,5950,"will feature a full set of BC Group jewelry."],[6273,6370,"Uncle Arman,"],[6546,6703,"for the first time, I wish"],[6706,6916,"that Gavin hadn't saved me back then."],[7143,7290,"Then he wouldn't be sick,"],[7463,7690,"and I never would have fallen in love with you."]],"65":[[393,620,"Arman, you're back just in time."],[659,843,"The kids just came and told me"],[855,1030,"that they want to get married sooner."],[1063,1200,"Hahaha."],[1566,1643,"Uncle Arman,"],[1646,1780,"after we get married,"],[1923,2126,"Anne will return to work at Sinclair Group."],[2270,2350,"Anne,"],[2530,2610,"what is the meaning of this?"],[2760,2850,"Uncle Arman,"],[2880,3153,"Gavin and I had a misunderstanding,"],[3226,3506,"but we've cleared it up now."],[3720,3800,"Hey,"],[4300,4380,"look at me."],[4566,4693,"I said, look at me."],[5340,5499,"Is he threatening you?"],[5887,5973,"No."],[6115,6195,"No."],[6303,6506,"I was always going to choose Gavin"],[6606,6713,"and marry him."],[6833,6930,"Is this the"],[6930,7036,"\"important thing\" you had to tell me?"],[7886,7954,"Uncle Arman,"],[7986,8253,"your nephew and niece-in-law cleared the air"],[8253,8360,"and are finally tying the knot."],[8460,8613,"You should be happy."],[8808,8888,"Gavin,"],[9063,9210,"what did you threaten her with?"],[9403,9483,"*Cough*,"],[9590,9726,"*cough, cough, cough*,"],[9864,10098,"*cough, cough, cough*."],[10193,10343,"Are you okay?"],[10430,10520,"*Cough, cough*."]],"66":[[2566,2646,"Mary,"],[2740,2866,"is Uncle Arman back?"],[2873,2946,"The Young Master moved all his"],[2950,3060,"things out today,"],[3060,3220,"saying he wants to live on his own."],[3260,3293,"Oh."],[3643,3723,"Anne."],[3933,4046,"Grandpa,"],[4046,4130,"you're back."],[4130,4240,"Grandpa,"],[4260,4440,"About Uncle Arman and that woman,"],[4453,4536,"maybe her"],[4540,4670,"husband found out,"],[4680,4863,"and she dumped him."],[4943,5050,"Grandpa, why"],[5053,5153,"would you think that?"],[5163,5306,"I went to check on him today."],[5343,5450,"He's lost a lot of weight,"],[5470,5590,"he's all scruffy,"],[5590,5690,"and in really bad shape."],[5690,5880,"He looks like he's heartbroken."],[5923,6100,"Is he eating properly?"],[6100,6180,"He's getting by."],[6186,6266,"But he did agree"],[6270,6396,"to meet the girl your aunt"],[6400,6546,"wants to set him up with."],[6803,6883,"Oh"],[6906,7100,"That's good news."]],"67":[[1223,1353,"Uncle Arman,"],[1353,1516,"why are you here again?"],[1563,1670,"You left the door open."],[1746,1936,"Doesn't that mean you wanted me to come in?"],[2182,2325,"I didn't."],[3973,4083,"Uncle Arman"],[4850,5016,"Arman, can we go?"],[5080,5230,"Anne, you're here."],[5270,5426,"This is Uncle Arman's girlfriend."],[5430,5570,"You used to be classmates."],[5573,5750,"Anne, long time no see."],[5823,5876,"Alright."],[5880,5956,"Let's go."],[6083,6220,"Okay. Gavin,"],[6223,6370,"Anne, see you next time."],[6573,6636,"Anne."],[6640,6756,"Uncle Arman and Miss Young"],[6760,6876,"seem to be getting along well."],[6880,7003,"When he came to Sinclair Group today,"],[7003,7170,"he moved everything out."],[7180,7356,"He won't be coming back to the company."],[7440,7573,"He gave up on Sinclair Group,"],[7673,7826,"and he gave up on me."]],"68":[[3,86,"Miss Young,"],[163,330,"I know my dad sent you to follow me,"],[333,420,"but it's useless."],[476,563,"I'm not interested."],[570,646,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[696,822,"why didn't you clarify just now"],[824,940,"that I'm not your girlfriend?"],[1116,1340,"Oh, you like your nephew's wife."],[1410,1673,"Don't be shocked. The way you look at her,"],[1673,1830,"even a child could tell how you feel."],[1833,2070,"But she and your nephew are deeply in love,"],[2083,2173,"so there's nothing you can do."],[2236,2420,"Since you can't have the one you love,"],[2453,2566,"and my family is pressuring me,"],[2570,2723,"why don't we make a deal?"],[2753,2946,"We help each other deal with our parents."],[3120,3246,"Mind your own business."],[3320,3413,"I'm not interested."],[3610,3743,"Arman!"],[3743,3876,"I want you,"],[3880,4003,"and I'm definitely going to get you."],[5743,5823,"Baby,"],[5880,6113,"what do you think Daddy is doing right now?"],[6170,6286,"Do you think"],[6286,6520,"he's having fun with that lady?"],[6788,6851,"Arman,"],[6893,6986,"I heard you gave up the fight"],[6990,7136,"for Sinclair Group's inheritance."],[7180,7290,"Is there a problem?"],[7310,7346,"No, but"],[7396,7473,"you gave up the promising future"],[7476,7540,"at BC Group abroad"],[7543,7683,"to come back and fight"],[7683,7840,"for the Sinclair family inheritance."],[7843,7960,"Why give it up now?"],[8223,8336,"I thought she wanted"],[8340,8586,"to be the lady of the Sinclair family."],[9103,9180,"Bro,"],[9263,9386,"if there were a Guinness World Record"],[9390,9540,"for being a lovestruck fool,"],[9556,9686,"I'll definitely sign you up."],[10173,10270,"You hopeless romantic."]],"69":[[900,990,"Anne."],[1010,1235,"Why has so much time passed"],[1240,1460,"without any progress on your project?"],[1460,1606,"Design requires inspiration."],[1606,1706,"You can't rush it."],[2193,2396,"Then why, at BC Group,"],[2410,2550,"when you were with Arman,"],[2560,2776,"did you produce one design after another?"],[3473,3673,"You're still thinking about Arman."],[3676,3923,"You just don't want to help me, do you?"],[4013,4053,"No."],[4053,4146,"Anne."],[4186,4310,"Have some shame."],[4330,4520,"He is my Uncle Arman!"],[4540,4716,"You're pregnant with his child."],[4723,4960,"Aren't you afraid of the scandal?"],[5140,5223,"Does Gavin know"],[5230,5360,"that I'm pregnant?"],[5370,5560,"I don't care how you do it,"],[5563,5750,"but the new Valentine's Day collection"],[5756,5900,"must beat BC Group's."],[5906,6053,"If you really can't draw anything,"],[6080,6300,"give BC Group's designs to Sinclair Group."],[6460,6540,"Impossible."],[6820,7010,"So you want the whole world"],[7013,7230,"to know how ungrateful you are?"],[7240,7356,"That behind my back,"],[7363,7516,"while I'm dying from saving you,"],[7540,7713,"you slept with Uncle Arman"],[7720,7953,"and got pregnant with his bastard?"],[8346,8446,"Anne."],[8540,8773,"My patience has limits."]],"70":[[70,140,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[203,293,"no one is fighting you"],[293,450,"for the Sinclair Group inheritance now."],[476,603,"Why are you still drowning your sorrows here?"],[703,970,"It's because of that b*tch, Anne."],[1103,1336,"She only cares about Arman,"],[1376,1553,"and has no intention of helping me."],[1570,1633,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[1660,1836,"how about we partner up?"],[1853,1990,"I can make Anne"],[1990,2196,"give up on Arman for good."],[2236,2380,"What's your plan?"],[2380,2510,"You steal Anne's phone,"],[2513,2643,"text Arman,"],[2656,2783,"and ask him to meet at a hotel."],[2850,3053,"Leave the rest to me."],[3200,3286,"Miss Young,"],[3350,3550,"you really want to be my aunt, don't you?"],[3820,4026,"- Pleasure doing business. - Pleasure."],[4150,4316,"After all our hard work these past few days,"],[4316,4500,"our market cap has reached $20 billion."],[4556,4723,"- Uncle Arman, I miss you. - Growth is up 25%."],[4730,4876,"- I'll wait for you at the hotel tonight. - We"],[4880,4956,"- Don't reply. - Next month"],[5300,5340,"Oh."],[5393,5550,"It's nothing. Carry on."],[6513,6636,"When did you get here?"],[6893,7026,"Just now."],[7050,7256,"I came to check on your progress."],[7466,7646,"The initial design draft is ready,"],[7663,7836,"but there are still some details,"],[7840,7970,"we need to discuss."],[8076,8223,"Thanks for the hard work, Anne."],[8756,8860,"I'll let you get back to it."],[8860,8946,"I'm heading out."]],"71":[[323,403,"Mr. Sinclair?"],[403,583,"Miss Sinclair sent you this room card."],[1516,1590,"Anne."],[4233,4313,"Hello?"],[4326,4373,"Anne,"],[4400,4533,"is Arman with you?"],[4606,4823,"I haven't seen Uncle Arman in days."],[4833,4940,"Has something happened?"],[4943,5093,"Arman was in a meeting this afternoon"],[5100,5266,"when he got your text to meet at a hotel,"],[5266,5360,"so he left to find you."],[5380,5510,"There's an emergency now,"],[5516,5623,"but I can't reach him."],[5690,5900,"I never sent Uncle Arman a message."],[6213,6440,"\"Uncle Arman, I miss you."],[6450,6593,"I'll wait for you at the hotel tonight."],[6650,6716,"Don't reply.\""],[6790,6913,"When did you get here?"],[7133,7263,"Just now."],[7266,7460,"I came to check on your progress."],[7526,7753,"It was Gavin who sent it."]],"72":[[143,226,"Uncle Arman."],[1753,1810,"Uncle Arman."],[1890,1963,"Uncle Arman."],[2166,2253,"Uncle Arman."],[4876,4986,"It's okay, it's okay."],[5194,5286,"Don't cry."],[6060,6140,"Uncle Arman."],[6343,6416,"I missed you."],[6733,6890,"I missed you so much too."],[7240,7493,"You texted asking me to come,"],[7550,7760,"so why are you late?"],[7843,8066,"I didn't send that text."],[8076,8203,"Are you okay?"],[8600,8816,"But did you want to text me?"],[9123,9180,"I"],[10256,10363,"Arman!"],[10366,10523,"I finally caught you."],[10523,10683,"I want to see"],[10686,10833,"which sl*t"],[10856,10990,"can summon you"],[10993,11126,"and dismiss you at will."]],"73":[[730,786,"Grandpa."],[796,850,"I"],[880,973,"Anne?"],[1026,1136,"Oh my."],[1193,1233,"Oh my God."],[1260,1566,"Disgraceful. Absolutely disgraceful."],[2293,2420,"I should have known."],[2476,2563,"You"],[2594,2664,"You"],[2690,2826,"It's okay."],[2930,3100,"I got him to come here on purpose."],[3146,3253,"I told him I was seeing a woman,"],[3256,3363,"rekindling an old romance,"],[3386,3463,"just to provoke him."],[3560,3750,"But why would you do that?"],[3790,3920,"Alright, alright."],[4046,4133,"Anne,"],[4193,4416,"there's nothing wrong with Gavin's health."],[4466,4573,"He's lying to you."],[4814,4917,"How do you know?"],[5036,5166,"Because I know"],[5263,5416,"you're still deeply in love with me."],[5740,5813,"Eat up."],[5910,6070,"Mister, are you the one"],[6070,6226,"that Anne likes?"],[6313,6450,"Why do you ask?"],[6583,6746,"Come here. Follow me."],[7480,7603,"Anne said"],[7603,7766,"this is the person she likes."],[7770,7993,"He looks just like you."],[8176,8343,"Did Anne draw this?"],[8399,8523,"Is this who she likes?"],[8560,8610,"Uh-huh."],[8620,8870,"She cried while drawing it."],[10616,10763,"So afterwards,"],[10956,11083,"you went to the orphanage?"],[11283,11466,"Then I investigated Gavin"],[11516,11620,"and found he was close"],[11623,11776,"with a doctor at that hospital."],[11776,11966,"His illness was completely faked."],[12540,12603,"Forget it."],[12650,12863,"He's got nothing left anyway."],[13406,13466,"Let's go."],[13480,13640,"Let's go back and explain it to Grandpa."],[13953,14080,"Didn't Grandpa just"],[14083,14246,"shut the door and leave?"]],"74":[[720,810,"Baby,"],[813,903,"look at your Great-Uncle,"],[910,1116,"working so hard."],[1446,1503,"Anne,"],[1610,1720,"what are you whispering?"],[1800,1890,"Nothing."],[2050,2130,"Come sit here."],[3513,3593,"Uncle Arman."],[3603,3673,"Don't think faking pain"],[3680,3816,"will get you off the hook."],[3843,3903,"No,"],[3940,4116,"I think my water broke."],[6083,6210,"It looks like the elevator's broken."],[6210,6290,"What do we do?"],[6583,6700,"Are you okay?"],[6766,6846,"What's wrong?"],[7250,7316,"Anne!"],[7416,7483,"Anne!"],[9573,9663,"Uncle Arman,"],[9856,9954,"three years ago, was it you"],[9956,10096,"who saved me from the elevator?"],[10173,10290,"You just figured that out?"],[10623,10820,"I always thought it was Gavin."],[10863,10986,"That's why I chose him"],[10986,11080,"for all those years."],[11153,11346,"I carried you down from floor twenty-something."],[11723,11873,"Thank you"],[11880,12026,"for loving me all this time."]]}